description:
Discover the epitome of refined elegance and exhilarating performance in this stunning 2023 Mercedes-Benz C-Class C 300. This meticulously maintained, certified pre-owned gem boasts a captivating Blue exterior, complemented by a wealth of premium features that elevate the driving experience to new heights.

Indulge in the exceptional amenities that set this C-Class apart:

• AMG® Line w/Night Package
• Exclusive Trim Package
• Parking Assist Package
• Sound Package
• Perforated Brake Discs
• Panorama Sunroof
• Active Distance Assist DISTRONIC®
• AMG® Body Styling
• AMG® Line Exterior
• Sport Suspension w/Sport Steering System
• Star Grille
• Enhanced Ambient Lighting
• Illuminated Door Sills
• Inductive Wireless Charging
• MB-Tex Dashboard

Elevate your driving experience with the exceptional performance of the 2.0L I4 Turbocharged engine, paired with a responsive 9-Speed Automatic transmission and rear-wheel drive. Enjoy exceptional fuel efficiency, with an EPA-estimated 25 MPG in the city and 36 MPG on the highway.

As a Mercedes-Benz Certified Pre-Owned vehicle, this C-Class comes with unparalleled peace of mind. Backed by a comprehensive 165+ point inspection, you can drive with confidence, knowing that every aspect of this car has been meticulously evaluated and approved. Additionally, you'll benefit from Roadside Assistance, a $0 Warranty Deductible, a Transferable Warranty, and a Limited Warranty that extends for 12 months or unlimited miles beyond the original factory warranty.

Discover the perfect blend of luxury, performance, and exceptional value in this 2023 Mercedes-Benz C-Class C 300. Experience the difference that Mercedes-Benz craftsmanship and attention to detail can make. Schedule a test drive today and let this exceptional vehicle captivate your senses.

description:
The 2020 Hyundai Kona Electric Ultimate is a fully electric compact SUV that offers impressive performance, a range of advanced features, and eco-friendly driving. Powered by an Electric Motor and paired with a 1-speed Automatic transmission, it delivers a smooth and efficient drive with front-wheel drive (FWD). The exterior is finished in Chalk White with a Black Roof, and the interior features Gray leather seating, providing a premium feel and comfort. The vehicle has 46,415 miles on the odometer as of January 2026.

This Hyundai and has been well-maintained with regular services, including the recent installation of new tires and new brakes. It has a clean one-owner history and has been maintained as part of the dealership's service loaner program. The CARFAX report indicates no accidents or damage, providing confidence in its condition.

Inside, the 2020 Kona Electric Ultimate is equipped with a variety of premium features, including a navigation system, an 8-speaker audio system, Apple CarPlay & Android Auto, a power moonroof, heated and ventilated front seats, and a backup camera. The vehicle also comes with a heads-up display, power driver seat, remote keyless entry, steering wheel-mounted audio controls, and an auto-dimming rearview mirror.

Safety features are a key priority in this model, including ABS brakes, dual front airbags, side airbags, electronic stability control, brake assist, low tire pressure warning, and rear parking sensors. The Kona Electric also comes with active cruise control, auto high-beam headlights, and rain-sensing wipers for added convenience and safety.

This 2020 Hyundai Kona Electric Ultimate is an excellent choice for anyone seeking a fully electric, well-equipped SUV with modern features, and it offers a reliable, eco-friendly option for daily driving.

Call (714) 647-2000 or visit https://www.tustinhyundai.com to schedule your test drive at Tustin Hyundai, located at 16 Auto Center Dr, Tustin, CA 92782. You will also enjoy no addendum, no dealer markups, an award-winning dealer experience, and a team dedicated to making your visit relaxed and enjoyable.

Discover the perfect blend of power, capability, and refined style with this 2020 GMC Sierra 1500 SLT. This impressive truck boasts an EcoTec3 5.3L V8 engine paired with a 10-speed automatic transmission and 4-wheel drive, delivering the performance and versatility you demand.

Key features include:
• Clean Carfax
• 20" Polished Aluminum Wheels
• X31 Off-Road Package with Off-Road Suspension, Hill Descent Control, and All-Terrain Tires
• Trailering Package
• 120-Volt Bed-Mounted Power Outlet

Step inside the spacious and well-appointed cabin, where you'll find premium amenities like heated and power-adjustable front seats, a heated steering wheel, and the advanced GMC Infotainment System with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto integration. The Sierra SLT also offers a suite of advanced safety technologies, including Forward Collision Alert, Lane Departure Warning, and Rear Vision Camera, to give you added peace of mind on the road.

Whether you're tackling tough jobsites, towing heavy loads, or simply enjoying the open road, this 2020 GMC Sierra 1500 SLT is ready to take on the challenge. With its impressive capability, refined interior, and distinctive style, this truck is the perfect blend of work and play. Schedule a test drive today and experience the power and versatility of the Sierra SLT for yourself.

This well-equipped Sierra SLT also features:
• 275/60R20 All-Terrain Tires
• Dual Exhaust with Premium Tips
• Integrated Trailer Brake Controller
• In-Vehicle Trailering App
• Hitch Guidance with Hitch View
• Front Frame-Mounted Black Recovery Hooks
• 120-Volt Instrument Panel Power Outlet
• 12-Volt Rear Auxiliary Power Outlet

Discover the ultimate combination of strength, technology, and comfort in this 2020 GMC Sierra 1500 SLT. Contact us today to schedule a test drive and experience the difference for yourself.

Take on every job and adventure with this 2020 GMC Sierra 1500 4WD SLT, finished in stunning Pacific Blue Metallic. This full-size truck combines rugged capability, advanced technology, and refined comfort, making it perfect for towing, hauling, or weekend getaways. Its bold exterior and commanding presence ensure you stand out wherever you go.

The X31 Off-Road Package equips this Sierra 1500 for any terrain, providing enhanced suspension, skid plates, and off-road-ready features for confident driving on and off the beaten path. A spray-on bedliner protects the cargo area, while chrome assist steps make entering and exiting the truck easy and stylish. Inside, heated and ventilated front seats deliver year-round comfort, and Adaptive Cruise Control helps maintain safe distances and reduces fatigue on highway drives.

With its combination of performance, capability, and advanced features, the 2020 GMC Sierra 1500 4WD SLT is a versatile and reliable truck ready for work or play.

Proudly serving McKinney, Allen, Plano, Frisco, The Colony and all of DFW and North Texas.

Here at Woody Anderson Ford we strive for transparency in our sales process. Our value pricing helps you take the guess work out of buying a vehicle, so grab an awesome deal on this good-looking 2024 Chevrolet Colorado LT while we have it. Spacious yet easy to maneuver, its great 8-Speed Automatic and its strong 2.7L I4 Turbocharged DOHC 16V LEV3-ULEV50 237hp engine have lots of personality for the money. It comes equipped with these options: Carfax 1-Owner, Heated Seats, Remote Start, Apple CarPlay/Android Auto, Blind Spot Monitor, Lane Keeping System. CARFAX One-Owner.

Certified. Certification Program Details: Ford Blue Advantage Blue Certified Pre-Owned means you not only get the reassurance of a 3 Mo/4,000-Mile comprehensive warranty, 139-point inspection/reconditioning, 24/7 roadside assistance, trip-interruption services, rental car benefits, and a complete CARFAX vehicle history report.

The most important part of buying a pre-owned vehicle is not the mileage or tires. The most important part of buying is trust. Woody Anderson Ford has been part of the community for over 50 years. So, if the thought of purchasing an used car makes you uneasy, maybe it's time to check us out. On the dash of every used car you will find a folder that contains detailed 169 point inspection, Kelley Blue Book and NADA value sheets for that vehicle! We don’t play games, we price our cars based on market based pricing and we offer that information to you up front! TRUST is a big word! Woody Anderson Ford will earn your trust! Two locations to serve you located in Huntsville and Madison Alabama. No pressure. Huge Selection! Great experience! Call, come see us or visit us at www.woodyandersonford.com.

description: Conquer the Road with Confidence: Discover the 2017 Chevrolet Silverado 1500 LT Crew Cab, Where Power Meets Precision in Every Mile Experience the perfect blend of power and sophistication with the 2017 Chevrolet Silverado 1500 LT. This used beauty is equipped with the robust Ecotec3 5.3L V8 engine, ensuring you have the muscle needed for any adventure. The sleek black exterior of this 4D Crew Cab exudes a commanding presence, while the 6-speed automatic transmission provides seamless shifting for a smooth ride. Safety is paramount with features like Stability Control, Traction Control, and a comprehensive airbag system, offering peace of mind on every journey. Enjoy modern conveniences with the Back-Up Camera and Bluetooth Connection, keeping you connected and secure. The leather steering wheel and heated mirrors add a touch of luxury, while the HD Radio and Satellite Radio ensure entertainment is at your fingertips. With Smart Device Integration and a WiFi Hotspot, stay connected wherever the road takes you. The Silverado s durable build and rear-wheel drive make it a reliable companion for both work and play, offering versatility and dependability in one impressive package. Whether navigating city streets or exploring rugged terrains, the Silverado 1500 LT is your ultimate driving partner. Be sure to call or visit Vandergriff Toyota to discover more. Your new favorite vehicle awaits - don't let someone else drive it home!

This impressive 2021 GMC Sierra 1500 AT4 is a rugged and capable truck that's ready to take on any adventure. Boasting a powerful EcoTec3 5.3L V8 engine paired with a smooth-shifting 10-speed automatic transmission, this Sierra AT4 delivers exceptional performance and efficiency, with an EPA-estimated 16 MPG in the city and 21 MPG on the highway.

• TECHNOLOGY PACKAGE: Includes HD Surround Vision, Rear Camera Mirror, Bed View Camera, and Multicolor 15" Diagonal Head-Up Display
• AT4 PREFERRED PACKAGE: Includes Universal Home Remote, Rear Sliding Power Window, Premium GMC Infotainment with Navigation, Bose Premium Audio System, and Wireless Charging
• DRIVER ALERT PACKAGE II: Includes Forward Collision Alert, Lane Keep Assist/Lane Departure Warning, Automatic Emergency Braking, Front Pedestrian Braking, IntelliBeam, Adaptive Cruise Control, and Following Distance Indicator

Elevate your driving experience with premium features like the Bose 7-speaker sound system, heated and ventilated front seats, and the convenient power sliding rear window. Stay connected with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto, and enjoy the added peace of mind from advanced safety technologies like Automatic Emergency Braking and Lane Keep Assist.

Whether you're tackling tough terrain or navigating the daily commute, this Sierra AT4 is built to impress. The rugged off-road suspension, 4-wheel drive, and locking rear differential ensure you can confidently conquer any challenge. And with the available Trailering Package, you'll have the capability to tow your toys with ease.

Boasting a stylish Gray exterior and a well-appointed interior, this 2021 GMC Sierra 1500 AT4 is a true head-turner. The bold, muscular design and premium features make this truck a standout in its class. Experience the difference for yourself and schedule a test drive today.

This Sierra AT4 is priced at $38,998, representing an exceptional value for a vehicle of this caliber. With its impressive capabilities, advanced technology, and premium amenities, this truck is sure to exceed your expectations. Visit our showroom and let us demonstrate why this Sierra AT4 is the perfect choice for your next adventure.

description:
Experience the power and capability of the 2020 Ford F-150 XLT. This exceptional truck is equipped with a robust 3.5L V6 EcoBoost engine, delivering the perfect balance of performance and efficiency. With its 4-wheel drive and 10-speed automatic transmission, you'll conquer any terrain with confidence, whether navigating city streets or tackling off-road adventures.

Highlighted features include:
• Equipment Group 302A Luxury
• Trailer Tow Package
• XLT Chrome Appearance Package
• XLT Power Equipment Group
• SiriusXM Radio
• Rear Window Defroster
• Power-Adjustable Pedals
• Upgraded Front Stabilizer Bar
• 2-Bar Style Grille with Chrome 2 Minor Bars
• Chrome Door & Tailgate Handles with Body-Color Bezel
• Chrome Step Bars

This F-150 XLT is more than just a workhorse - it's a true companion that elevates your driving experience. The spacious and well-appointed interior features premium cloth seating, power-adjustable front seats, and a leather-wrapped steering wheel, creating a refined and comfortable environment. Stay connected with the voice-activated touchscreen navigation system and enjoy the convenience of the 110V/400W outlet.

Towing and hauling capabilities are enhanced with the Trailer Tow Package, which includes a Class IV trailer hitch receiver, Pro Trailer Backup Assist, and an integrated trailer brake controller. Whether you're transporting heavy loads or towing your favorite toys, this F-150 is up to the task.

Designed with your safety in mind, the F-150 XLT comes equipped with a suite of advanced driver-assistance technologies, including a Reverse Sensing System, LED box lighting, and an auto-dimming rearview mirror. You can navigate with confidence, knowing you have the support you need.

Experience the unparalleled capabilities and refined comfort of the 2020 Ford F-150 XLT. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate how this exceptional truck can elevate your driving experience. We're confident you'll be impressed by its impressive performance, versatility, and attention to detail.

Discover the perfect blend of power, capability, and style with this 2022 Ford Ranger XLT. This exceptional mid-size pickup boasts an impressive array of features that make it the ultimate companion for your adventures.

• One Owner
• Accident Free CarFax
• Locally Owned New Car Trade
• AWD/4WD
• Cruise Control
• Steering Wheel Controls
• CarPlay
• Android Auto
• Bluetooth

Equipped with the EcoBoost 2.3L I4 GTDi DOHC Turbocharged VCT engine and a 10-Speed Automatic transmission, this Ranger delivers exceptional performance and efficiency, with an impressive 19 MPG in the city and 24 MPG on the highway. The 4WD system ensures you can tackle any terrain with confidence, while the Trailer Tow Package allows you to haul your gear with ease.

The interior of this Ranger XLT is packed with premium amenities, including Leather-Wrapped Steering Wheel, Auto-Dimming Rearview Mirror, and a 110V AC Power Outlet. The Sport Appearance Package adds a touch of sporty style with Magnetic Painted Front & Rear Bumper, Black Mesh Grille, and Magnetic Painted Fender Vent Surround.

Safety is a top priority, and this Ranger is equipped with a host of advanced features, including Dual Front Impact Airbags, Dual Front Side Impact Airbags, Electronic Stability Control, and a Rear View Camera. The SYNC 3 infotainment system with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto keeps you connected and entertained on the go.

Whether you're tackling the daily commute or embarking on a weekend adventure, this 2022 Ford Ranger XLT is the perfect companion. With its impressive performance, versatile capabilities, and premium features, it's a truck that's built to impress. Visit our showroom today and experience the power and style of the Ranger for yourself.

• 1 Owner Clean CarFax
• Utility Pickup Shell
• Popular Equipment Group
• Tradesman Package

The Tradesman trim level offers a host of practical amenities, such as SiriusXM Satellite Radio, remote keyless entry, and a ParkView Rear Back-Up Camera, ensuring your daily driving and towing tasks are a breeze. Enjoy the comfort of the cloth 40/20/40 split bench seat, complete with front and rear floor mats for added protection.

This Ram 1500 Classic also comes equipped with a suite of advanced safety features, including ABS brakes, dual front impact airbags, and electronic stability control, providing you and your passengers with peace of mind on the road.

As a certified pre-owned vehicle, this 2023 Ram 1500 Classic Tradesman has undergone a rigorous 125-point inspection and comes with a comprehensive warranty package. Enjoy the benefits of a like-new vehicle, including 24-hour roadside assistance, a CARFAX Vehicle History Report, and a 3-month trial subscription to SiriusXM Satellite Radio.

With its impressive capabilities, practical features, and the added assurance of the certified pre-owned program, this 2023 Ram 1500 Classic Tradesman is the perfect choice for those seeking a reliable and versatile pickup. Experience the confidence and convenience of owning this exceptional vehicle. Visit our showroom today to take it for a test drive and make it your own.

Step inside the driver focused cockpit with premium sports seats, a high resolution digital display, Bose premium audio, and seamless Apple CarPlay and Android Auto connectivity to keep you connected every mile. description:
Conquer Every Terrain with Confidence: Discover the 2023 GMC Canyon AT4 in Sterling Metallic, Engineered for Adventure and Built to Impress
The 2023 GMC Canyon AT4, dressed in a sleek Sterling Metallic finish, is a powerhouse designed for those who seek adventure without compromise. Its 2.7L Turbo engine, paired with an 8-speed automatic transmission, delivers robust performance and efficiency, ensuring you&rsquor,re ready for any journey. The four-wheel drive system, coupled with a locking/limited slip differential, provides exceptional traction and control, making it perfect for off-road enthusiasts and city dwellers alike.
Safety is paramount in the Canyon AT4. Equipped with advanced features like Front Collision Mitigation, Lane Keeping Assist, and Automatic Highbeams, this vehicle ensures peace of mind on every drive. The intuitive Back-Up Camera and Tow Hooks add practicality, whether navigating tight city streets or rugged trails.
Inside, comfort meets technology with heated front bucket seats, a power driver seat, and a user-friendly interface featuring Bluetooth connectivity, Satellite Radio, and a WiFi Hotspot. The Smart Device Integration and Remote Engine Start enhance convenience, making every drive seamless.
The GMC Canyon AT4 is not just a truck, it&apos,s a statement of capability and style, crafted for those who demand more from their vehicle.

Why BUY from BMW of Lafayette? When you choose this Alpine White 2020 BMW 8 Series 840i with 57,723 miles, you are not just buying a used vehicle - you are investing in quality, reliability and peace of mind. Our clientele depend on us for Transparent Pricing, Convenience and, most importantly, Customer FIRST Service! No Accidents! One Owner! What this vehicle includes: Driving Assistance Package ($1,100 value)
  • Active Driving Assistant
  • Parking Assistant Plus
  • Drive Recorder
  • Active Blind Spot Detection
  • Lane Departure Warning
  • Active Park Distance Control
  • Rear View Camera
  • Surround View with 3D View
Safety and Security
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
  • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
Technology and Telematics
  • Apple CarPlay Compatibility smart device wireless mirroring
  • Mobile hotspot - WiFi on the fly. Connect your devices to the Internet through your vehicle's private mobile hotspot and take the internet wherever your journey takes you, without eating up your data allowance. Find the hotspot with mobile hotspot.
Come on in to BMW of Lafayette today at 178 Sagamore Parkway South Lafayette IN 47905 or call to schedule a test drive!

description:
Discover the perfect blend of power, capability, and style with this 2010 Ford F-150 XLT. This rugged and well-equipped truck is ready to take on any challenge, whether you're hauling heavy loads, tackling off-road adventures, or simply enjoying the open road.

• Premium Wheels
• Premium Audio
• Fully Serviced by Factory-Trained Technicians
• Tow Package
• Local Trade
• Driver's Group
• GVWR: 6,950 lbs Payload Package
• Trailer Tow Package
• XLT Chrome Package
• XLT Convenience Package
• Navigation System
• Auxiliary Transmission Oil Cooler
• Remote Keyless Entry
• Traction Control
• ABS Brakes
• Low Tire Pressure Warning
• Electronic Stability Control
• Rear-View Camera

Under the hood, the powerful 4.6L V8 EFI 24V engine, paired with a smooth-shifting 6-speed automatic transmission, delivers impressive performance and efficiency. With 4-wheel drive capabilities, this F-150 is ready to tackle any terrain with confidence.

The exterior of this F-150 XLT exudes a commanding presence, thanks to the bold White paint and chrome accents. The premium wheels and chrome-tipped exhaust add a touch of style, while the fog lamps and chrome door handles with black bezels enhance the overall visual appeal.

Step inside and you'll be greeted by a well-appointed interior, featuring premium cloth seating, a leather-wrapped steering wheel, and a host of convenient features. The 6-way power driver's seat and adjustable pedals ensure a comfortable driving position, while the rear-view camera and parking sensors make maneuvering a breeze.

Connectivity is also a priority, with the AM/FM stereo, CD player, and available navigation system keeping you entertained and informed on the go. The dual-zone climate control and power windows and locks add to the overall comfort and convenience.

This 2010 Ford F-150 XLT is a true workhorse, ready to take on any challenge you throw its way. With its impressive capabilities, thoughtful features, and striking appearance, it's the perfect companion for your next adventure. Visit our showroom today and experience the power and versatility of this exceptional truck for yourself.

Convenience
  • Cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful, until cruise control set the pace. Simply set the desired speed using the steering wheel mounted controls and it will maintain that speed without driver intervention. This can help minimize driver fatigue and improve overall fuel economy. Resting your right foot is right at your fingertips thanks to cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls.
Safety and Security
  • Brake assist - Stop right there. Something jumps out into the middle of the road and you need to stop now! With brake assist, you will. It uses the speed of the brake pedal's travel to sense panic braking, then applies all available power to boost your stopping power. Brake assist can stop the accident before it is one.

description: Explore this rugged and dependable 2017 Chevrolet Silverado 1500 Work Truck, a versatile pickup designed to handle both work and play with ease. Finished in a pristine Summit White exterior complemented by a durable Dark Ash interior with Jet Black accents, this used truck boasts a reliable 5.3L V8 engine producing 355 horsepower and 383 lb-ft of torque. Equipped with a smooth 6-speed automatic transmission and rear-wheel drive, it delivers a commanding driving experience. Whether you're towing, hauling, or commuting, this Silverado offers an impressive 16 mpg city and 23 mpg highway, making it a practical choice for daily use. Modern convenience features such as Bluetooth connectivity, a trailer tow package, and xenon headlights make every trip safer and more enjoyable. The addition of a 110V AC power outlet, a 7-inch diagonal color touchscreen with Chevrolet MyLink, a comprehensive rear vision camera system, and heavy-duty trailer equipment enhances its functionality and user experience. With deep-tinted glass and the WT Convenience Package, this Silverado is well-equipped to meet your needs with style and reliability. Built for safety and security, the 2017 Chevrolet Silverado 1500 includes essential features to keep you protected on the road. It offers a rear seat reminder to enhance passenger safety, along with 4-wheel anti-lock brakes (ABS) for improved stopping power in diverse conditions. The truck features power door locks with anti-lockout functionality and auto-locking capability to prevent unauthorized access, providing peace of mind for vehicle security. Additionally, the programmable safety key allows you to customize security settings or restrict access, making this truck a secure workhorse for various applications. 2017 Chevrolet Silverado 1500 Entertainment and Technology Features This Silverado is equipped with six total speakers that deliver clear and balanced sound throughout the cabin, ensuring an enjoyable driving experience. The auxiliary audio input via USB allows seamless connection of your favorite devices, enabling you to listen to your music, podcasts, or audiobooks effortlessly. These entertainment features, combined with the advanced MyLink touchscreen system, make this truck not only powerful but also connected and enjoyable for every journey. 2017 Chevrolet Silverado 1500 Performance Features One of the standout performance features of this Silverado is its cylinder deactivation technology. This system allows the engine to automatically deactivate half of the cylinders when full power is not needed, improving fuel efficiency without sacrificing performance. This advanced feature helps maximize economy during highway cruising or light-load driving, making the Silverado 1500 an efficient and capable pickup that doesn't compromise on power or reliability. Whether you're tackling tough jobs or enjoying weekend adventures, this 2017 Chevrolet Silverado 1500 Work Truck offers a compelling mix of power, technology, and safety. Its comprehensive features and proven durability make it an excellent choice for drivers seeking a reliable and well-equipped used pickup.

Experience the epitome of luxury and performance in this stunning 2018 BMW 5 Series 530i xDrive. This meticulously maintained vehicle boasts a sleek white exterior and a spacious, well-appointed interior that will captivate you from the moment you step inside.

Highlighted by an impressive array of features, this 5 Series delivers unparalleled comfort and convenience. Enjoy the luxurious touch of the Black Dakota Leather upholstery, complete with contrast stitching and piping. The Park Distance Control and heated front seats provide an added layer of sophistication, while the 19-inch V-Spoke (Style 635) wheels with run-flat tires offer a commanding presence on the road.

• Black, Dakota Leather Upholstery with Contrast Stitching and Piping
• Park Distance Control
• Wheels: 19" x 8" V-Spoke (Style 635) with 245/40R19 All-Season Run-Flat Tires
• Heated Front Seats

• Space-Saver Spare

Beneath the sleek exterior lies a powerful 2.0L 4-cylinder engine paired with an 8-speed automatic transmission and xDrive all-wheel-drive system. This dynamic powertrain delivers an exceptional blend of performance and efficiency, with an EPA-estimated 23 mpg in the city and 33 mpg on the highway.

The 5 Series is equipped with a wealth of advanced technologies to enhance your driving experience. Enjoy the convenience of the Navigation System, the clarity of the 12-speaker HiFi Sound System, and the seamless connectivity of the Enhanced USB & Bluetooth features. The Active Driving Assistant and Rear-View Camera provide added peace of mind, while the Panoramic Moonroof and Heated Steering Wheel add a touch of luxury.

This 2018 BMW 5 Series 530i xDrive is a true testament to the brand's commitment to exceptional craftsmanship and performance. With its stunning appearance, impressive capabilities, and comprehensive list of premium features, this vehicle is sure to captivate any discerning buyer. We invite you to schedule a test drive and experience the unparalleled joy of owning this exceptional BMW.

description: Discover the perfect balance of utility and style with the 2022 Ford Maverick XLT. This compact pickup boasts a remarkable combination of features that make it an exceptional choice for those seeking a versatile and capable vehicle.Highlighted by the FX4 Off-Road Package, this Maverick XLT is equipped to handle any terrain with ease. Enjoy the added confidence of Hill Descent Control, skid plates, and 17-inch all-terrain tires, while the 400W inverter and full-size spare tire provide added convenience and peace of mind. The 8-speed automatic transmission with AWD ensures seamless power delivery, while the EcoBoost 2.0L I4 engine delivers an impressive 22 city/29 highway MPG.• FX4 Off-Road Package• 400W Inverter• Front & Rear Floor Liners w/o Carpet Mats• Engine Block Heater• Trailer Hitch Receiver w/4-Pin Connector• 6.5 Productivity Screen in Instrument ClusterThe Maverick XLT's interior is designed with your comfort and convenience in mind. Enjoy the intuitive controls, including steering wheel-mounted audio buttons, as well as the 6-speaker audio system with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto integration. Stay connected and informed with the onboard technology, including the rearview camera and automatic high-beam headlights.Safety is a top priority, and the Maverick XLT delivers with a suite of advanced features. Dual front and side impact airbags, ABS brakes, and electronic stability control work together to provide a secure driving experience. The Occupant Sensing Airbag system and Brake Assist further enhance your protection on the road.Whether you're tackling off-road adventures or navigating the daily commute, the 2022 Ford Maverick XLT is the perfect companion. With its impressive capabilities, thoughtful design, and advanced safety features, this compact pickup is ready to elevate your driving experience. Visit our showroom today and discover the true versatility of the Maverick XLT.

Safety and Security
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
  • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
  • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.

Discover unbeatable selection and small-town customer care at Westgate Chevrolet and Westgate Chrysler Dodge Jeep Ram, two full-service dealerships sharing one location in Burgaw, NC. With a huge inventory of new Chevy, Chrysler, Jeep, Dodge, and Ram models, plus one of southeastern North Carolina's best selections of quality used cars, trucks, and SUVs. Westgate delivers transparent pricing and a hassle-free buying experience for every shopper.

• SPORT APPEARANCE PACKAGE
• LARAMIE LEVEL 1 EQUIPMENT GROUP
• 5.7L V8 HEMI
• BLACK, LEATHER TRIMMED BUCKET SEATS

This 2020 Ram 1500 Laramie is a rugged and refined pickup that's ready to take on any challenge. With its powerful 5.7L HEMI V8 engine, this Ram delivers exceptional performance and capability, while the Sport Appearance Package adds a bold, athletic style. Inside, the Laramie trim pampers you with premium leather-trimmed bucket seats, an 8.4-inch touchscreen infotainment system, and a host of advanced safety and convenience features.

The exterior of this Ram 1500 commands attention with its body-colored front and rear bumpers, door handles, and exterior mirrors, along with a sport performance hood and unique sport decal. The 20-inch premium painted wheels with inserts complete the sporty, yet sophisticated look. Step inside and you'll be greeted by the handsome black leather interior, complete with power-adjustable and heated front seats, a heated steering wheel, and dual-zone automatic climate control.

Safety and technology are also priorities in this Laramie model. Blind Spot and Cross Path Detection, ParkSense front and rear park assist, and a rearview camera help you navigate with confidence, while features like remote tailgate release, auto high-beam headlamps, and rain-sensing windshield wipers add convenience to every drive.

Whether you're hauling the family, towing a trailer, or seeking a premium, capable daily driver, this 2020 Ram 1500 Laramie has the power, capability, and comfort to exceed your expectations. Experience the difference for yourself and schedule a test drive today.

Serving Burgaw, Wilmington, Jacksonville, and all of southeastern NC, Westgate Chevrolet and Westgate Chrysler Dodge Jeep Ram offer one of the region's strongest selections of new Chevy, Chrysler, Jeep, Dodge, and Ram vehicles—along with a massive inventory of used cars, trucks, and SUVs for every budget. With transparent pricing and a reputation for honest, customer-focused service, Westgate is your trusted source for both new and used vehicles in North Carolina.

Every vehicle at Westgate comes pre-installed with Recovr vehicle location technology and professional window tint, included for a total cost of $799.

2025 Mercedes-Benz G-Class AMG G 63 4MATIC
MANUFAKTUR Arabian Grey - AMG Performance Package - One Owner - Only 10,799 Miles
With its unmistakable presence and handcrafted AMG performance, this 2025 Mercedes-Benz G 63 AMG 4MATIC stands as the pinnacle of off-road-capable luxury. Finished in $6,500 MANUFAKTUR Arabian Grey Non-Metallic over Titanium Grey Pearl/Black Nappa Leather, this G 63 boasts a rare combination of sophistication and aggression. Under the hood lies a handcrafted 577-hp AMG 4.0L V8 biturbo engine, delivering commanding acceleration with a thunderous exhaust note, while AMG ACTIVE RIDE CONTROL suspension ensures refined dynamics on any surface.

This G 63 comes exceptionally equipped with over $31,000 in factory options, highlighted by:
Factory Options & Packages:
- AMG Performance Package AMG Drivers Package, AMG TRACK PACE, red brake calipers, and more ($4,400)
- Night Package Plus Gloss black exterior accents, dark chrome AMG grille, Obsidian Black exhaust & body styling ($4,250)
- MANUFAKTUR Interior Package Plus Superior Line Interior, Active Multicontour Seat Package Plus, Nappa leather dash ($8,250)
- ENERGIZING Comfort Package Plus Wellness programs combining seat massage, climate, fragrance, and lighting
- 22" AMG Matte Black Forged Monoblock Wheels with Obsidian Black spare wheel ring ($4,650)
- AMG Performance Steering Wheel Nappa leather & microfiber grip for enhanced feel ($500)
- Metal Weave Trim + Piano Black Console + MANUFAKTUR Interior Touches
- MANUFAKTUR Roof in Obsidian Black + Bumper Insert + Running Boards
- Wheel Locking Bolts + Rubber Mat Set + Full Transport Protection
Original MSRP: $217,845
Comparable new 2026 models with similar equipment now price near $225,000+.
Condition & History:
- Only 10,684 miles well below average for a 2025 model
- 1-owner vehicle, originally registered in New Jersey
- Fully documented dealer maintenance history, including oil service and multi-point inspections as recently as January 2026
- Clean CARFAX, no accidents or damage reported
- Still under Mercedes-Benz 4-year/50,000-mile New Vehicle Warranty, estimated to remain active until April 2029 or ~39,300 miles (confirm exact details with dealer)

description:
Theres a deliberate kind of drama to the 2022 BMW X6 xDrive40i the automotive equivalent of a tailored suit with an unexpected flourish. It arrives as if on cue: a coupelike roofline that slices the horizon, hips that broaden into a confident stance and surfacing that plays with light like a sculpture catching a sunset. It isnt shy about presence, rather, it choreographs it. From some angles its athletic, from others almost aristocratic a crossover that has learned how to be both predator and patron of the pavement.

Approach and the details reward a slow look. The face is assertive but refined, the grille and lamps arranged less for flash and more for attitude. The sweep of the shoulder, the tucked rear, the way the wheels fill their arches all suggest motion even when the car is politely stationary. Its a silhouette designed to age well: bold enough to be noticed, tasteful enough to keep you noticing.

Slide in and the cabin feels like a private study crafted for motion. Materials are chosen for touch and temperament soft leather, purposeful stitching, and trim that catches light without shouting. The cockpit wraps around the driver with an inviting focus, controls fall naturally to hand and the seating encourages a posture thats both commanding and comfortable. Ambient lighting and a quiet acoustic palette make the interior feel like a sanctuary where conversation, music and concentration coexist with ease.

On the road the X6s personality reveals itself in layered ways. Steering is authoritative, turning directional intent into composed action, the chassis balances poise with playful willingness, ready to tighten when you ask and to smooth when you dont. Acceleration is confident rather than theatrical, delivering momentum with a dignified immediacy that invites engagement without demanding it. The soundtrack is measured a low, persuasive growl that underscores movement rather than dominates it.

Technology and convenience are integrated with discretion: helpful, contemporary and designed to enhance the experience rather than distract from it. Practical touches abound without spoiling the mood, luggage space and seating flexibility keep errands practical while preserving the cars dramatic temperament.

In short, the 2022 BMW X6 xDrive40i is a study in controlled charisma: sculptural presence, refined interiors and a driving demeanor that rewards intention. Its a car that wants to be noticed, but only because it knows how to deserve the attention.

Experience the Uncompromising Capability of the 2025 GMC Canyon AT4

Elevate your driving experience with the 2025 GMC Canyon AT4, a rugged and refined midsize truck that's ready to conquer any terrain. Boasting a powerful 2.7L Turbo I4 engine delivering 310 horsepower, this Canyon AT4 is engineered to tackle the toughest challenges with ease. Paired with an 8-speed automatic transmission and formidable 4-wheel drive, this truck is a true off-road champion.

• Nightfall Edition: Includes rocker panel protectors, all-terrain tires, black badges, and more for an aggressive, blacked-out look.
• AT4 Premium Package: Elevates your comfort with perforated leather-appointed seating, heated and ventilated front seats, a heated steering wheel, and a suite of premium features.
• 6-Speaker Audio System, 11.3" Premium Infotainment System, Wireless Apple CarPlay/Android Auto, and Wireless Charging for seamless connectivity on the go.
• Rocker Panel Protector, Black Badges, and 20" Machined-Face Aluminum Wheels for a bold, distinctive style.
• Heated and Ventilated Front Seats, Heated Steering Wheel, and Driver Memory Recall for unparalleled comfort and convenience.

This Canyon AT4 doesn't just look the part—it's engineered to deliver exceptional off-road capability and on-road refinement. With a rugged suspension, off-road tires, and advanced driver-assist technologies, you'll conquer the trail with confidence. And with the premium interior, advanced connectivity, and thoughtful utility features, you'll enjoy every mile, whether you're tackling the daily commute or embarking on your next adventure.

Why BUY from BMW of Lafayette? When you choose this Alpine White 2026 BMW X3 30 xDrive with 1,306 miles, you are not just buying a used vehicle - you are investing in quality, reliability and peace of mind. Our clientele depend on us for Transparent Pricing, Convenience and, most importantly, Customer FIRST Service! No Accidents! One Owner! What this vehicle includes: Premium Package ($3,450 value)
  • Remote Engine Start
  • Heated Steering Wheel
  • Panoramic Moonroof
  • Travel and Comfort System
  • Interior Camera
  • Driving Assistance Plus
  • Parking Assistant Plus
  • BMW Curved Display with HUD
  • Premium Content 1
  • Distance Control (ACC) with Steering Assistant
  • Parking View with 3D View (Surround View)
Driving Assistance Professional Package ($1,700 value)
  • Driving Assistant Professional
  • Traffic Jam Assistant
  • Distance Control (ACC) with Steering Assistant
  • Lane Change Assistant
Convenience
  • Unresponsive driver assistant - a reaction to inaction. Maybe you fell asleep. Maybe you lost consciousness. No matter how it happens, Unresponsive driver assistant works to help lessen the danger when it does. It detects prolonged driver unresponsiveness, automatically bringing the vehicle to a stop and turning on the hazard lights. If equipped, emergency services will also be contacted. Unresponsive driver assistant is safety that never sleeps.
Safety and Security
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
Technology and Telematics
  • Apple CarPlay and Android Auto Compatibility smart device wireless mirroring
  • Mobile hotspot - WiFi on the fly. Connect your devices to the Internet through your vehicle's private mobile hotspot and take the internet wherever your journey takes you, without eating up your data allowance. Find the hotspot with mobile hotspot.
Come on in to BMW of Lafayette today at 178 Sagamore Parkway South Lafayette IN 47905 or call to schedule a test drive!

description:
Sport-Lux Daily Driver, AWD Confidence 2022 BMW 228i xDrive Gran Coupe

This 2022 BMW 228i xDrive Gran Coupe at Zeigler Lincolnwood Campus Cadillac | Buick | GMC is finished in Black Sapphire Metallic over Black SensaTec, delivering sharp BMW style with all-weather traction and a tech-forward cockpit.
A strong Chicagoland commuter pick for drivers who want compact performance feel, premium features, and confident winter capability.

Key Highlights

  • xDrive AWD + STEPTRONIC Automatic: Confident traction in rain and snow with smooth, responsive shifting for daily driving.

  • Sport Line + Sport Seats: A more aggressive look and a tighter, more supportive driving position that feels distinctly BMW.

  • Live Cockpit Pro w/Navigation: Modern digital displays and built-in navigation for a clean, upscale driving interface.

  • Convenience Package: Adds the right comfort upgrades to make every day easier and more premium.

  • Panoramic Moonroof: Brightens the cabin and elevates the overall luxury feel.

  • Remote Engine Start: Warm up or cool down the cabin before you step inperfect for Midwest seasons.

  • Heated Front Seats + Heated Steering Wheel: Cold-weather comfort that youll use constantly in real life.

  • Driver Assist Tech: Active Guard, lane departure warning, blind spot detection, forward collision warning, and dynamic cruise control for calmer daily miles.

  • Parking Support: Rear view camera + Park Distance Control to make tight parking feel simple and controlled.

  • Apple CarPlay/Android Auto Compatibility: Seamless smartphone integration for maps, calls, and music.



Why It Stands Out
Black Sapphire over Black is the clean, stealth spec that always looks right. With xDrive AWD, Sport Line, Live Cockpit Pro, pano roof, remote start, and heated comfort features, this 228i is dialed for Chicago seasons while still feeling fun and premium behind the wheel. Available now near Chicago, IL with nationwide shipping for out-of-state buyers.

Dealer Assurance
Every vehicle at Zeigler Lincolnwood Campus Cadillac | Buick | GMC is inspected, detailed, and ready for your driveway.
We proudly serve drivers from Lincolnwood, Chicago, and across the U.S. with nationwide delivery available.

Act fast xDrive Gran Coupes with this black-on-black spec and tech package mix are in high demand. Call today to schedule your VIP test drive or arrange delivery.

Conquer every road in this 2025 Jeep Grand Cherokee L Limited 4x4, finished in striking Bright White. This full-size SUV combines rugged capability with refined luxury, offering three rows of comfort and the advanced features you need for every journey.

Inside, enjoy premium comfort with heated front and second-row seats, ensuring every passenger stays cozy on chilly days. The spacious cabin provides versatile seating and cargo options, making it perfect for family trips, weekend getaways, or daily errands.

Advanced technology keeps you confident on the road, including Adaptive Cruise Control and Active Lane Management, which help maintain safe distances and lane positioning for a smoother, stress-free drive. The Remote Start System adds convenience, allowing you to pre-warm or pre-cool the cabin before you step inside.

With capability, comfort, and cutting-edge features, the 2025 Grand Cherokee L Limited 4x4 is ready to handle any adventure in style.

Proudly serving McKinney, Allen, Plano, Frisco, The Colony and all of DFW and North Texas.

This 2024 Chrysler Pacifica Limited is a remarkable family-friendly vehicle that combines exceptional versatility, advanced safety features, and premium amenities. With its sleek white exterior and spacious interior, this Pacifica is the perfect companion for your growing family's adventures.

The heart of this Pacifica is its powerful 3.6L V6 engine, which delivers an impressive 19 city/28 highway MPG, ensuring efficient performance for your daily commute and long road trips alike. The 9-speed automatic transmission provides smooth and responsive shifting, making every drive a pleasure.

One of the standout features of this Pacifica is the PANORAMIC ROOF, which floods the cabin with natural light and enhances the sense of openness and airiness. The SAFETY SPHERE package, including the 360 Surround View Camera System and Parallel & Perpendicular Park Assist, provides an exceptional level of confidence and peace of mind when maneuvering in tight spaces or navigating busy city streets.

The Uconnect 5 infotainment system with a 10.1-inch display keeps you connected and entertained, seamlessly integrating with your smartphone via Apple CarPlay and Android Auto. The heated steering wheel, heated and ventilated front seats, and premium audio system ensure a comfortable and enjoyable driving experience for you and your passengers.

This vehicle is Certified by Bill Luke! Bill Luke Certified vehicles are backed by a 3 month/3000 mile limited powertrain warranty and a 7-Day/150 mile buyback guarantee!

BILL LUKE SANTAN is a family owned and operated business that has done business the right way since 1927. You can buy with confidence! Unlike some of our competitors, our RECONDITIONING COSTS are INCLUDED in the sales price. Bill Luke Santan's price is based on Kelley Blue Book Price AdvisorTM - which allows you to see what other Arizona residents have paid for the same year, make and model of vehicle while considering vehicle mileage. See dealer for details or visit www.billlukesantan.com to see the difference for yourself!

description:
Discover the perfect blend of style, comfort, and convenience with this stunning 2016 Honda HR-V EX-L w/Navigation. This sleek and versatile SUV is the ideal choice for those seeking a vehicle that can seamlessly adapt to their dynamic lifestyle.

Boasting an impressive array of features, this HR-V is equipped to elevate your driving experience. Highlights include:
• Honda Satellite-Linked Navigation System
• 6 Speakers
• AM/FM radio: SiriusXM
• CD player
• Automatic temperature control
• Power moonroof
• Heated front seats
• Leather Seat Trim

Step inside and be captivated by the luxurious leather-trimmed interior, which provides a refined and sophisticated ambiance. The heated front seats ensure your comfort, while the spacious cabin offers ample room for both passengers and cargo.

Powered by a 1.8L I4 SOHC 16V i-VTEC engine and equipped with an advanced CVT transmission, this HR-V delivers a smooth and efficient ride, with an impressive 27 city/32 highway MPG. The all-wheel-drive system provides enhanced traction and stability, making it the perfect companion for all your adventures.

Designed with your safety in mind, this HR-V is equipped with a suite of advanced safety features, including ABS brakes, dual front impact airbags, and Electronic Stability Control. You can drive with confidence, knowing that you and your loved ones are well-protected.

At Brickell CDJR, we understand that finding the right pre-owned vehicle can be a daunting task. That's why we've made it our mission to provide you with a stress-free and enjoyable buying experience. Our team of experts is dedicated to ensuring that you find the perfect vehicle to suit your needs and budget.

Don't miss your chance to own this exceptional 2016 Honda HR-V EX-L w/Navigation. Visit us at 701 SW 8th St, Miami, FL 33130, or call 305-777-2800 to schedule a test drive and experience the difference for yourself.

At Brickell CDJR, we make buying a pre-owned vehicle easy and stress-free. Every pre-owned vehicle is thoroughly inspected to ensure quality and reliability. For added confidence, we include a **10-year/100,000-mile powertrain warranty on all non-European brands** at no additional cost. Our dealership offers one of the largest selections of pre-owned inventory in the region, so you can find the right car, truck, or SUV for your needs. Our state-of-the-art service department, the largest in the country, is open seven days a week from 7 AM to 9 PM, ensuring your vehicle stays in top condition. Visit us at 701 SW 8th St, Miami, FL 33130, or call 305-777-2800 to learn more and schedule a test drive. The displayed price includes an incentive for financing with Brickell CDJR Finance Company. Price does not included our Perma-Plate .Outside financing and bank drafts are not accepted. All pre-owned vehicle exports are subject to an export fee. Taxes, title, registration, and dealer fees apply.

The 2019 BMW 5 Series 530i Sedan in Alpine White exemplifies elegance and sophistication with its sleek design and commanding presence on the road. Powered by a 2.0L 4-cylinder engine, this sedan promises a dynamic driving experience, combining efficiency with impressive performance. The vibrant LED headlights enhance visibility, while the rain sensing wipers ensure a clear view during inclement weather. Inside, the Black Sensatec leatherette upholstery exudes luxury, providing both comfort and style for all passengers. Apple CarPlay integration and Bluetooth connectivity keep you seamlessly connected, allowing for effortless access to your favorite media and navigation through the advanced system. The heated front seats offer added warmth during colder months, ensuring driver and passenger comfort on every journey. Safety features are abundant, highlighted by the blind spot monitor and lane departure warning, which offer peace of mind during every mile traveled. The inclusion of a hands-free liftgate and power tailgate ensures convenience when accessing the trunk, making the sedan as practical as it is luxurious. Topping off the experience, the Convenience Package provides additional features like telematics, promising a ride that's as smart as it is comfortable. The 2019 BMW 530i Sedan not only meets your driving expectations but elevates them with its blend of style, comfort, and innovation. ***Fantastic Condition***

Vehicle Details
2018 Subaru Forester Touring AWD — 4-Cylinder 2.0L Gasoline, located in Hinesville, GA. This well-maintained Subaru Forester Touring blends refined comfort with rugged capability, featuring Subaru's Symmetrical All-Wheel Drive and a fuel-efficient 2.0L four-cylinder engine for confident year-round performance. The premium leather seats and spacious interior deliver upscale comfort for driver and passengers, while automatic climate control keeps the cabin comfortable on every drive.

Equipped with advanced technology, this Subaru Forester includes navigation and XM Radio to keep you connected and entertained on long trips. Adaptive Cruise Control enhances highway driving by maintaining a safe following distance, reducing driver fatigue on commutes and road trips. Practical Subaru engineering and a thoughtfully designed cargo area make this vehicle ideal for families, outdoor enthusiasts, and daily commuters.

Safety-focused features and the AWD system provide reliable traction in variable weather, making this Subaru Forester a smart choice for Georgia seasons. The vehicle is competitively priced and represents the best price available locally—an exceptional value for its features and condition. Located in Hinesville, GA, this 2018 Subaru Forester Touring is ready for test drives and immediate pickup. Bluetooth technology is built into this mid-size suv, keeping your hands on the steering wheel and your focus on the road. Our dealership has already run the CARFAX report and it is clean. Discover the perfect blend of versatility and sophistication in this 2018 Toyota RAV4 XLE. With its sleek black exterior and a well-appointed interior, this SUV is ready to elevate your driving experience.

• Remote keyless entry

Powered by a 2.5L 4-Cylinder DOHC Dual VVT-i engine and equipped with All-Wheel Drive, this RAV4 delivers an impressive balance of performance and efficiency, with an EPA-estimated 22 MPG in the city and 28 MPG on the highway.

Beyond its impressive capabilities, this RAV4 XLE is packed with a wealth of premium features that cater to your every need. Enjoy the convenience of the Entune Display Audio system, dual-zone automatic climate control, and the versatility of the 60/40 split-folding rear seats. The power moonroof and blind spot monitoring system add an extra layer of sophistication and safety, while the alloy wheels and roof rails enhance the vehicle's sporty and adventurous appeal.

Whether you're navigating the daily commute or embarking on a weekend getaway, this 2018 Toyota RAV4 XLE is the perfect companion. Its spacious interior, advanced technology, and exceptional driving dynamics make it a standout in the compact SUV segment. Experience the difference for yourself and schedule a test drive today. We're confident you'll be impressed by the exceptional value and quality this RAV4 has to offer.

As you consider your next vehicle, we encourage you to visit our showroom and explore the 2018 Toyota RAV4 XLE in person. Our knowledgeable sales team is here to answer any questions you may have and help you find the perfect SUV to suit your lifestyle. We're committed to providing a seamless and enjoyable car-buying experience, so you can drive away with the confidence and peace of mind you deserve.

description:
Discover the perfect blend of style, performance, and versatility with this exceptional 2024 Mazda CX-5 2.5 S Preferred Package. This sleek and sophisticated SUV is the embodiment of Mazda's commitment to crafting vehicles that captivate the senses and elevate the driving experience.

Boasting a stunning MACHINE GRAY METALLIC exterior, this CX-5 exudes a refined and modern presence that is sure to turn heads wherever you go. Under the hood, the powerful 2.5L I4 DOHC 16V LEV3 SULEV30 engine delivers an impressive 187 horsepower, seamlessly paired with a 6-Speed Automatic transmission and Mazda's renowned all-wheel-drive system, ensuring a smooth and confident ride.

• MACHINE GRAY METALLIC PAINT
• Power Liftgate
• Rear Bumper Guard
• Multifunction Commander Control
• Pandora
• SMS Text Msg Audio Delivery & Reply
• Leather Seat Trim
• Heated Front Bucket Seats
• Power driver seat
• Power passenger seat

The CX-5's impressive fuel efficiency, with an EPA-estimated 23 MPG in the city and 29 MPG on the highway, makes it an exceptional choice for both your daily commute and weekend adventures. Slip behind the wheel and experience the responsive handling, precise steering, and the refined, well-appointed interior that sets this Mazda apart from the competition.

Designed with your comfort and convenience in mind, the CX-5 2.5 S Preferred Package boasts a wealth of premium features, including dual-zone automatic climate control, a power moonroof, and a state-of-the-art infotainment system with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto integration. description:
Experience the Pinnacle of Luxury and Capability with the 2022 Jeep Grand Cherokee L Limited

Introducing the 2022 Jeep Grand Cherokee L Limited, a true masterpiece of automotive engineering that seamlessly blends unparalleled capability, sophisticated style, and cutting-edge technology. This exceptional SUV is poised to redefine your driving experience, offering a level of refinement and versatility that will captivate even the most discerning of drivers.

Key features of this remarkable vehicle include:
• Dual Pane Panoramic Sunroof
• Interior Rear Facing Camera
• Front Passenger Interactive Display
• Pur Wrapped Instrument Panel
• Uconnect 5 NAV with 10.1" Display

The 2022 Jeep Grand Cherokee L Limited is powered by a robust 3.6L V6 24V VVT engine, mated to an 8-Speed Automatic transmission and equipped with 4-Wheel Drive, delivering an exceptional balance of performance and efficiency. With an EPA-estimated 18 MPG in the city and 25 MPG on the highway, this SUV offers the perfect blend of power and fuel economy.

Step inside the cabin and be welcomed by a world of luxurious comfort and convenience. The Capri Leather-trimmed seats, heated front and rear seats, and a heated steering wheel ensure a truly indulgent driving experience, no matter the weather. The 10.1" Touchscreen Display with Uconnect 5 Navigation provides seamless connectivity, while the 506-Watt Amplifier and 9 Amplified Speakers with Subwoofer deliver a concert-quality audio experience.

Designed to handle any adventure with confidence, the 2022 Jeep Grand Cherokee L Limited is equipped with a host of advanced safety features, including a ParkView Rear Back-Up Camera, Adaptive Cruise Control, and Blind Spot Monitoring with Rear Cross-Path Detection. These cutting-edge technologies work in harmony to keep you and your loved ones safe on the road.

Whether you're embarking on a family road trip, navigating the urban jungle, or tackling the great outdoors, the 2022 Jeep Grand Cherokee L Limited is the perfect companion. Experience the pinnacle of luxury and capability today by scheduling a test drive at our showroom. We're confident that once you get behind the wheel, you'll never want to settle for anything less.

Power Liftgate, Back-Up Camera, Turbocharged, iPod/MP3 Input, CD Player, Onboard Communications System Rear Spoiler, MP3 Player, Privacy Glass, Child Safety Locks.

WHY BUY FROM US
Buy with confidence at Group 1 where every used vehicle, up to 175,000 miles, comes with a one month 1,000-mile limited warranty along with a 3-day 250-mile return policy. Some exclusions may apply, see Buyers Guide for specifics. Every vehicle is priced to market and includes a Carfax History Report.

NO HAGGLE, NO HASSLE PRICING
When buying a pre-owned vehicle, Group 1 Automotive keeps things simple. You get competitive, up-front pricing based on live data pulled from more than 20,000 websites, updated hourly. No pricing games. No inflated numbers. No back-and-forth negotiation. Just market-based pricing you can trust.

MARKET-BASED PRICING
You expect fair & competitive pricing. Thats why the price is based on current market data and is regularly compared to similar pre-owned vehicles in the region.

QUALITY INSPECTIONS
Every vehicle is thoroughly inspected and comes with a complimentary vehicle history report.

QUICK & TRANSPARENT FINANCING
Need Financing? Apply in minutes with all terms and conditions clearly disclosed upfront.

VEHICLE SERVICE CONTRACTS
Avoid bumps in the road! Adding a service contract can help prevent future unexpected expenses from arising. Available for most purchases.

EXPERTS REPORT
Most Benzes lean toward stately power and control, but the GLA is one of the more fun and raucous models in the Mercedes lineup. Its like a powerful Subaru XV Crosstrek. -Edmunds.com.

description: Capable by nature, our 2020 Land Rover Defender 110 HSE AWD in Eiger Grey Metallic is luxurious by design! Motivated by a TurboCharged and electrically SuperCharged 3.0 Liter 6 Cylinder generating 395hp paired to an 8 Speed Automatic transmission for boosted acceleration backed by mild-hybrid efficiency. This four-door All Wheel Drive SUV taps into a Terrain Response system to leave the beaten path far behind, and it scores nearly 22mpg on the highway with premium LED headlights, fog lamps, a panoramic sunroof, power-folding heated mirrors, functional roof rails, and 20-inch alloy wheels. Our HSE keeps you comfortable even in rough conditions thanks to leather heated/ventilated power front seats, a power-adjustable leather-wrapped steering wheel, and keyless entry with an exposed powder-coated cross-car beam that adds robust strength while doubling as a handy shelf. You'll also appreciate the high-tech benefits of a 12.3-inch digital instrument panel, a 10-inch touchscreen, full-color navigation, Android Auto,, Apple CarPlay,, Bluetooth,, and an 11-speaker Meridian sound system. Land Rover provides smart safety measures like a surround-view camera system, automatic braking, lane-keeping assistance, adaptive cruise control, and a blind-spot monitor to safeguard your adventures. A fantastic fusion of form and attitude, our Defender 110 HSE is a re-imagined icon. Save this Page and Call for Availability. We Know You Will Enjoy Your Test Drive Towards Ownership!. description: Experience the Refined Sophistication of the 2014 Kia Sorento LXThis stunning 2014 Kia Sorento LX is a true testament to Kia's commitment to quality and innovation. With its sleek exterior design, advanced technology features, and impressive performance capabilities, this versatile SUV is poised to exceed your expectations.• LX Convenience Package (5 Seat) - Includes Backup Warning System, Heated Front Seats, Auto Dimming Rear View Mirror w/Compass, Roof Rails, Leather Wrapped Steering Wheel & Gear Shift Knob, Carpet Floor Mats (5 Seat), 2nd Row Sunscreen, UVO Audio w/eServices & Backup Camera Display, Fog Lamps• 6 Speakers, AM/FM/CD/MP3 Audio System, Air Conditioning, Power Windows, Remote Keyless Entry, Steering Wheel Mounted Audio Controls, Traction Control, ABS Brakes, Dual Front Airbags, and morePowered by a 2.4L I4 DGI DOHC Dual CVVT engine and equipped with an efficient 6-Speed Automatic with Sportmatic transmission, this Sorento LX delivers a smooth and responsive driving experience. The leather-wrapped steering wheel and gear shift knob, along with the auto-dimming rearview mirror with compass, add a touch of sophistication to your daily commute.Enhance your driving experience with the advanced UVO audio system, featuring a backup camera display and eServices for seamless connectivity. The Sorento LX also boasts a suite of safety features, including a backup warning system, ABS brakes, and a comprehensive airbag system, ensuring your peace of mind on the road.With its sleek design, impressive performance, and extensive list of premium features, the 2014 Kia Sorento LX is a true standout in the SUV segment. Experience the refined sophistication of this exceptional vehicle and schedule your test drive today.WHY BUY FROM ROB GREEN NISSAN HYUNDAIEvery vehicle receives an intensive multi-point inspection in our world-class service centerAll work completed by factory-trained, certified techniciansOne full year of free maintenance included with every purchaseTrusted, locally owned dealership committed to exceptional customer care

Introducing the all-new 2019 Jeep Cherokee Latitude Plus! This versatile and stylish SUV is here to elevate your driving experience. With its sleek design, advanced technology, and impressive performance, the Cherokee Latitude Plus is the perfect vehicle for any adventure.

Step inside and you'll immediately notice the spacious and comfortable interior, complete with premium cloth seats and plenty of legroom for all passengers. The Uconnect 4 infotainment system allows for seamless connectivity to your favorite devices, and the 8.4-inch touchscreen display makes it easy to navigate.

Under the hood, the Cherokee Latitude Plus packs a punch with its 2.4L Tigershark MultiAir 2 engine, delivering up to 180 horsepower and 171 lb-ft of torque. This SUV also comes equipped with Jeep's legendary 4x4 system, ensuring a smooth and capable ride no matter the terrain.

But the 2019 Jeep Cherokee Latitude Plus isn't just about performance, it also prioritizes safety. With features like blind spot monitoring, rear cross path detection, and a rearview camera, you can drive with confidence and peace of mind.

Don't miss your chance to own the ultimate SUV. Visit your local dealership and test drive the 2019 Jeep Cherokee Latitude Plus today. With its stunning design, cutting-edge technology, and unbeatable performance, it's the perfect choice for those who want to stand out on the road. Hurry, limited stock available!

description: Experience the perfect blend of sport-inspired performance and sophisticated luxury in this 2023 Audi A5 Sportback 45 S line Premium. Dressed in a crisp Ibis White, this vehicle features the powerful 45 TFSI engine paired with Audi's legendary quattro all-wheel drive system. Whether you are navigating a rainy highway or enjoying a winding backroad, you'll appreciate the confidence and stability that comes with this high-performance setup.Step inside to a cabin that defines modern elegance, featuring Leather Seating Surfaces and genuine wood accents on the console and dashboard. This A5 Sportback is designed for year-round comfort, offering Heated Front Sport Seats and a Heated Steering Wheel for those colder mornings. The three-zone automatic climate control ensures that everyone, including rear passengers, stays at their preferred temperature, while the power moonroof provides an airy, open feel to every drive.Technology is at the heart of the Audi experience. This model comes equipped with the Convenience Package, which includes Adaptive Cruise Control to make long highway trips effortless and Audi Side Assist (blind-spot monitoring) for added safety. You'll also enjoy the convenience of the Audi Advanced Key, a Power Liftgate for easy cargo access, and SiriusXM w/360L to keep your favorite entertainment within reach.This CARFAX One-Owner vehicle is as smart as it is beautiful. description:
Our highly capable One Owner 2021 Chevrolet Tahoe Z71 4WD with the Z71 Off-Road Package can help your whole family go farther, and it stands out pretty far itself in Black! Powered by a 5.3 Liter V8 that delivers 355hp to a 10 Speed Automatic transmission for easy towing and passing. Also returning nearly 20mpg on the highway, this rugged Four Wheel Drive SUV is well-equipped for the trail with a two-speed transfer case, a front skid plate, hill-descent control, magnetic ride control suspension, air ride adaptive suspension, and red front tow hooks. Even our Tahoe's front bumper is optimized for off-road conditions. Designers add a panoramic sunroof, black chrome accents, LED lighting, and alloy wheels for visual flair, with a hands-free liftgate for upscale convenience.

Our Z71 cabin showcases comfortable accommodations with heated leather power front seats, versatile second/third rows, a heated leather-wrapped steering wheel, tri-zone automatic climate control, keyless start, and advanced technologies for your digital needs. Charge your phone, connect to Android Auto/Apple CarPlay without the hassle of wires, and take advantage of a 10.2-inch touchscreen, WiFi capability, Bluetooth, and a Bose audio system. And there's room for plenty of cargo, too!

Safeguarding your travels are Chevrolet features such as automatic emergency braking, forward-collision warning, a following-distance indicator, rear parking sensors, and an HD rearview camera. Our Tahoe Z71 is built with you in mind! Save this Page and Call for Availability. We Know You Will Enjoy Your Lifted Trucks Katy Test Drive Towards Ownership! Lifted Trucks has built an unmatched reputation over the last two decades for customizing and selling thousands of the highest quality used vehicles in the country. Our inventory is nationally sourced by our certified buyers who cherry pick only the best of the best of what is available. These vehicles then go through an 82 point inspection process to guarantee quality and safety. Our lift kits are installed by our own factory-trained technicians, who have thousands of hours of experience. The installation is then inspected by a second dedicated quality control technician, before being sent to our state of the art Hunter Engineering laser alignment rack. Our aftermarket research and development team always matches the best fitting lift kit, shocks, and wheel & tire combinations to each individual vehicle for optimal off-road performance, while maintaining an incredibly smooth ride on the street. We never cut any corners on our builds, which is why we only use top quality name brand products when building your Truck, SUV or Jeep. Lifted Trucks has thousands of 5-star reviews, and one of the highest rates of repeat customers in the auto industry. Stop by today, and experience the difference.

description:
2022 Audi RS 5 The Glacier-Forged Dragon of Ingolstadt

From the frozen forges of Audi Sport there came a creature of impossible balance.

A dragon sculpted not from scales, but from sheet metal and starlight.

Her name is RS 5, and she wears Glacier White Metallic, a color that gleams like the hide of some mythical beast birthed in the highest Alps, cold to the eye and hot to the touch.

She was traded in against a Golf R, but not because she was outmatched.
No.
Only because some souls are called to different forms of magic.

Inside her chest beats a 2.9 liter twin-turbocharged V6, a heart tuned by runes and engineers to summon 444 horsepower.
When stirred, it does not purr.

It exhales flame, crackling and roaring through the forested roads of the West Coast, where she lived her life under gentle weather and careful stewardship.

Her past is spotless. CARFAX One Owner. Clean CARFAX.
Her condition is immaculate.
Her cause is speed.
Her power channels through an eight-speed Tiptronic that strikes with lightning precision.
Her traction comes from quattro, that ancient Audi sorcery which binds earth and tire, clawing through every season with unflinching command.
Inside, she is not savage. She is royal.
She carries Fine Nappa Leather stitched in Crescendo Red, a pattern that looks almost ceremonial, like the markings of a noble house.
Her S Sport seats cradle riders like saddles meant for war.
Her heated steering wheel warms the hands of the knight who dares command her.
Her 19-speaker sound system fills the cabin with music worthy of a hall of kings.
The Black Optic Package tempers her beauty with shadow.
High gloss black mirrors, spoilers, and diffusers glint like obsidian plating.
Her 20-inch forged Flag-Design wheels turn like twin crests, sharp and defiant.
Her mind is keen and watchful.
Adaptive Cruise Control with Traffic Jam Assist.
Active Lane Assist.
Park Assist.
Top View Camera System.
Traffic Sign Recognition.
A Head-Up Display that projects the roads prophecy onto the air before her.
And when she opens her power moonroof, the sky peers inside, as if curious about the creature beneath.
She is the product of the RS mind.
Part speed.
Part grace.
Part winter.
Part fire.
She is the Glacier-Forged Dragon, the firebreather dressed in ice,
returned now to your halls and awaiting the next worthy rider. Come shop at Carter VW Today!

description:
The 2024 Toyota Highlander in Celestial Silver Metallic offers a perfect balance of style, comfort, and advanced technology in a midsize SUV. Its sleek exterior is complemented by 18" alloy wheels, giving it a modern and confident presence on every road.

Inside, the Highlander is designed for family comfort and convenience, featuring reclining third-row seats to ensure all passengers enjoy a relaxed ride. Connectivity is seamless with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto, keeping you linked to navigation, music, and hands-free communication no matter where your journey takes you.

Safety and visibility are enhanced with Auto Highbeams, automatically adjusting to traffic conditions for safer nighttime driving. Combined with Toyota's reputation for reliability, the Highlander provides peace of mind for every trip.

A stylish, versatile, and tech-savvy SUV that meets the demands of modern families with comfort, capability, and confidence.

Proudly serving McKinney, Allen, Plano, Frisco, The Colony and all of DFW and North Texas.

description: Makes & Models is proud to present this 2021 Audi RS 7 finished in Mythos Black Metallic over a Black with Express Red stitching interior. Powering the RS 7 from this year is the industry staple 4.0L Twin-Turbocharged V8 paired with a 48-volt Mild-Hybrid assist laying down 591 HP and 590 lb-ft of torque straight from the factory. With the lighting fast shifts of the 8-Speed Tiptronic transmission, the 2021 RS 7 gets to 60 PMH from a standstill in just 3.5 seconds.To add to the madness, this vehicle has a Stage 1 APR Tune installed, bringing the total HP 685+ based on APR's information. Also installed are Integrated Engineering Carbon Fiber Intakes, adding to the induction sound immensely.From the factory, this RS 7 was equipped with $22,225 in all the best options. Inside, you have the Driver Assistance package and Executive package, Bang & Olufsen Advanced 3D Sound, Black Alcantara Headliner, and the Carbon Twill inlays.Outside, you'll see the Carbon Optic Package, Steel Red Brake Calipers, Sport Exhaust, and the Audi Guard Protection kit.In December of 2025, Makes & Models completed a 4 wheel alignment, inspection, coolant breather line replacement, and the passenger tie rod. New front brakes and brand new tires were also installed in December of 2025 through Big O Tires.This RS 7 has 2 keys, brand new tires, only 3 owners, and every option you'd ever want. Along with the recent service history, tasteful modification, and all original literature, this RS 7 is ready for it's next home.At Makes & Models, we make the buying process simple for both local and out-of-state buyers. We offer financing options up to 144 months with rates starting at 5.49%, and we can assist with open or enclosed transport anywhere in the country. Use your lender or ours, either way, we handle all paperwork electronically for a fast, smooth transaction Call or text our team at 801-546-2277 to learn more or schedule a time to see it. Safety and Security
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
  • Hands-off cruise control - Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful. Cruise control only managed speed, but not distance or safety. Now with hands-off cruise control simply set your desired speed and let sensor technology maintain a safe distance between you and surrounding vehicles with minimal steering input from you. It slows you down, speeds you up and even keeps you in your own lane. Meet your ultimate co-pilot with hands-off cruise control.
Technology and Telematics
  • Audi smartphone interface w/wireless Apple CarPlay smart device wireless mirroring
  • Mobile hotspot - WiFi on the fly. Connect your devices to the Internet through your vehicle's private mobile hotspot and take the internet wherever your journey takes you, without eating up your data allowance. Find the hotspot with mobile hotspot.
To be sure you don't miss out, give us a call at (888) 685-1813 and schedule a test drive. We are located at 139 N Oregon Street Sanford FL 32771. We look forward to seeing you soon.

The 2023 Audi S5 Sportback 3.0T Quattro Prestige is a high-performance luxury vehicle, offering a blend of style, power, and advanced features.
