description: Finding a clean 280ZX Turbo is hard. Finding one like this is almost unheard of!This 1981 Datsun 280ZX Turbo shows just 31,000 original miles and presents in true collector-quality condition throughout. Finished in timeless silver over blue velour seating, it perfectly captures the era when Nissan blended grand touring comfort with genuine turbocharged performance and did it with style.Powered by the legendary L28ET turbocharged inline-six, this ZX delivers smooth, torque-rich acceleration and the unmistakable character that made the Turbo models the ones to have. This example has been climate-controlled stored since new, and it shows everywhere you look from the paint and trim to the interior materials that feel remarkably preserved.The interior is a standout, with plush blue velour seats that remain vibrant and supple, free of the wear you typically see even on low-mileage cars. All T-top seals are perfect, a major point for any 280ZX buyer, and the car includes the rare factory fog lights, adding both desirability and period-correct presence.What truly elevates this car is the documentation. It comes with complete original paperwork, including the window sticker and original marketing collateral, underscoring how carefully this ZX has been preserved from day one.This isn t a restored example it s an original survivor, and those are becoming nearly impossible to find at this level. For the serious collector or enthusiast who understands the importance of mileage, originality, and provenance, this 280ZX Turbo is a must-see and a cornerstone-quality addition to any collection.Financing and nationwide delivery available$1050 doc fee applies to all salesIn business over 30 years Vantage Auto offers both unique inventory and fresh trade ins offered at wholesale to the public pricing. Be sure to check out our Instagram, @VantageAutoCollection!

  • This \'intelligent\' cruise control system uses laser or radar to maintain a preset following distance behind another vehicle, automatically braking (to a complete stop if needed) or accelerating as required.
Safety and Security
  • With this system the driver's hands must remain on the wheel at all times but can be removed briefly (for a few seconds), otherwise the vehicle will prompt the driver to put their hands back on the wheel.
  • The vehicle is equipped with a system that senses, and then prepares, the vehicle and/or occupants, for an impending forward collision.
  • The vehicle constantly monitors the roadway in front of the vehicle and identifies and tracks pedestrians on an interior display. If the system determines a likely impact, it will automatically take preventative steps to avoid hitting the pedestrian.
  • The vehicle is equipped with a camera that displays an image of the area behind the vehicle on an interior display. The camera is equipped with its own washer.
  • An active lane departure system alerts the driver of unintended movement of the vehicle out of a designated traffic lane and automatically maintains the vehicle's position within that lane.
Technology and Telematics
  • Apple CarPlay/Android Auto smart device wireless mirroring
  • Mobile devices can wirelessly connect to the internet through the vehicle's private mobile network.

description: Introducing the 2023 Jeep Grand Cherokee Summit, a versatile and sophisticated SUV designed for both urban adventures and off-road excursions. This model is powered by a robust Pentastar 3.6L V6 engine, delivering 293 horsepower and 260 lb-ft of torque, ensuring a smooth and capable driving experience on various terrains. The exterior of the Grand Cherokee Summit showcases a refined design, featuring a bold front grille, sleek LED headlights, and distinctive chrome accents that exude luxury. The vehicle sits on stylish 20-inch wheels, contributing to its commanding presence on the road. Inside, the Grand Cherokee Summit is equipped with a spacious and upscale cabin that prioritizes comfort and convenience. Premium leather upholstery adorns the seating, with heated and ventilated front seats providing year-round comfort. The driver and front passenger can enjoy adjustable power seating with memory functions for personalized comfort. The centerpiece of the interior is the advanced Uconnect infotainment system, displayed on a large 10.1-inch touchscreen. This system integrates navigation, Apple CarPlay, and Android Auto, allowing for seamless connectivity and access to your favorite apps and music. A premium audio system enhances the driving experience, delivering crystal-clear sound throughout the cabin. Safety features are a cornerstone of the Grand Cherokee Summit, with an array of advanced technologies designed to protect occupants. Standard safety equipment includes adaptive cruise control, blind-spot monitoring, lane departure warning, and forward collision warning with automatic emergency braking, ensuring peace of mind on every journey. Additionally, the vehicle comes equipped with a panoramic sunroof, allowing natural light to fill the cabin and offering stunning views of the sky above. The hands-free liftgate provides easy access to the spacious cargo area, making loading and unloading a breeze. With its blend of luxury, performance, and safety, the 2023 Jeep Grand Cherokee Summit stands out as a top choice for those seeking a premium SUV that can handle both everyday driving and adventurous escapades.Although every reasonable effort has been made to ensure the accuracy of the information contained on this site, absolute accuracy cannot be guaranteed. 2021 Audi RS 5 2.9T – Pure Performance, Stunning Style, Audi Precision
The 2021 Audi RS 5 2.9T isn’t just a car—it’s a high-performance masterpiece built for drivers who crave speed, precision, and head-turning style. Powered by a 2.9L twin-turbo V6 engine, this RS 5 delivers 450 horsepower and instant torque, propelling you from 0 to 60 mph in just over four seconds. Coupled with Audi’s legendary quattro® all-wheel-drive system, the RS 5 offers exceptional traction, confident cornering, and precise handling that make every drive exhilarating, whether you’re hitting the track or cruising city streets.
The exterior design of the 2021 RS 5 commands attention at every angle. Its aggressive front grille, wide stance, and aerodynamic body lines announce performance without saying a word. RS-specific styling cues, sharp LED headlights, and available black optic packages elevate the sportiness, making this coupe impossible to ignore. Every detail is engineered for both speed and style, reflecting Audi’s commitment to precision and performance.
Step inside, and the cabin is a blend of luxury and sportiness. RS sport seats, premium leather and Alcantara accents, and an RS-branded steering wheel create a driver-focused environment that puts you in complete control. The Audi Virtual Cockpit, MMI® infotainment system, and advanced connectivity options keep you connected, informed, and entertained, while ambient lighting and ergonomic design ensure every drive is as comfortable as it is thrilling.
Safety and technology are never compromised. The 2021 RS 5 comes equipped with advanced driver-assistance features, including adaptive cruise control, lane departure warning, and collision mitigation systems, so you can push the performance without sacrificing peace of mind. This is a car for enthusiasts who demand luxury, performance, and precision in one beautifully engineered package.
For those who want a sports coupe that combines raw power, luxurious comfort, and jaw-dropping style, the 2021 Audi RS 5 2.9T is the ultimate choice. Every corner, straightaway, and drive becomes an opportunity to experience pure automotive exhilaration.

Why Buy from Paragon Honda? When you choose this 2021 Honda Civic Type R Limited Edition from Paragon Honda, you're not just buying a car - you're securing one of the most collectible modern Hondas ever built. This Limited Edition Type R represents the final and most track-focused version of the legendary FK8 generation, produced in extremely limited numbers and finished in the iconic, exclusive Phoenix Yellow Pearl. This example is also a true collector piece: Limited Edition badge #200. With just 215 original miles, this is about as close to factory-new as it gets. Located in Woodside, NY 11377, we're proud to offer one of the best selections of pre-owned Honda vehicles and top-tier used cars in the Queens area. Here's why savvy buyers trust us: Why This Type R Limited Edition Is Special
  • Ultra-Rare Limited Edition - Highly limited production with limited U.S. allocation
  • Collector Detail: Limited Edition badge #200
  • Last & Lightest FK8 Type R - Weight-reduction measures for a more track-focused feel
  • Phoenix Yellow Pearl - Exclusive Limited Edition color
  • Turbocharged Performance - 306-hp 2.0L VTEC Turbo + 6-speed manual transmission
  • Track-Ready Hardware - Brembo brakes, adaptive suspension, and precision handling
  • Extremely Low Miles - 215 miles
No Accidents!
One Owner! PHOENIX YELLOW, BLACK/RED, SUEDE-EFFECT FABRIC SEATING SURFACES Transparent Ownership Benefits
  • Transparent Pricing: At $$59,995, what you see is what you pay.

    • 7yr/100k Powertrain limited warranty from original in-service date

    • Two complimentary oil changes will be offered
    • XM 3 months free trial period
    • Trip interruption
  • Customer-First Service: Our award-winning team treats you like family, backed by an excellent customer satisfaction rating.
  • Convenience: Complimentary pick-up and delivery for service and sales, plus easy financing options to make car buying stress-free.
  • Also for your convenience: Our service department is open 24 hours a day, 7 days a week.
Safety and Security
  • Forward collision mitigation - Helps detect potential frontal collisions and can assist in reducing severity.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - Monitors the road ahead to identify pedestrians and can take steps to help avoid a collision.
  • Rear camera - Enhanced visibility of what's behind you for safer reversing.
Technology and Telematics
  • Smart device mirroring - Integrates your smartphone with the infotainment system to improve convenience and help keep focus on the road.
Ready to drive home this 2021 Honda Civic Type R Limited Edition today at Paragon Honda in Queens, NY? Call us at 718-550-1710 to schedule your visit. Discover the Pinnacle of Hybrid Efficiency and Sophistication: The 2025 Toyota Prius XLE

Elevate your driving experience with the remarkable 2025 Toyota Prius XLE, a masterpiece of engineering and design. This exceptional hybrid vehicle combines unparalleled fuel efficiency, advanced technology, and a refined, spacious interior to deliver a driving experience that will captivate you from the moment you take the wheel.

• Remote keyless entry
• Traction control
• ABS brakes
• Low tire pressure warning
• Electronic Stability Control
• Heated door mirrors
• Illuminated entry
• Alloy wheels
• AM/FM radio: SiriusXM
• Air Conditioning
• Automatic temperature control
• Rear window defroster
• Power steering
• Power windows
• Steering wheel mounted audio controls

Boasting an impressive 52 MPG in both city and highway driving, the Prius XLE sets a new standard for eco-conscious performance. Its 2.0L 4-Cylinder DOHC 16V VVT engine, paired with a Continuously Variable (ECVT) transmission, delivers a seamless and responsive driving experience, allowing you to glide effortlessly through your daily commute or weekend adventures.

Step inside the Prius XLE and be captivated by the refined and spacious cabin, designed with your comfort and convenience in mind. Enjoy the convenience of features like remote keyless entry, heated door mirrors, and illuminated entry, while the alloy wheels and sleek exterior styling exude a sense of modern sophistication.

The Prius XLE also comes equipped with a host of advanced safety features, including Traction Control, ABS Brakes, Low Tire Pressure Warning, and Electronic Stability Control, ensuring your peace of mind on the road. With the added protection of dual front impact airbags, dual front side impact airbags, and an emergency communication system, you can drive with confidence, knowing that your safety is a top priority.

Experience the future of hybrid technology today with the 2025 Toyota Prius XLE. This exceptional vehicle offers a seamless blend of efficiency, technology, and style, making it the perfect choice for the discerning driver who demands the best. Visit our showroom and let us demonstrate how the Prius XLE can transform your driving experience.

Customer-First Service: Our award-winning team treats you like family, backed by an excellent customer satisfaction rating. Convenience: From complimentary pick-up and delivery for sales and service, to easy financing options, we make car buying stress-free. **Certified Pre-Owned** One Owner! Included with Purchase: 7-Day Vehicle Exchange - Full Tank of Gas - 3 Oil and Filter Changes - 3 Tire Rotations - Car Washes - $500 Collision Deductible Reimbursement Policy - Pickup & Delivery for Sales & Service! Important Package and Feature Information Safety and Security
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
  • Hands-on cruise control. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful. Cruise control only managed speed, but not distance or safety. Now, with hands-on cruise control, simply set your desired speed and let sensor technology maintain a safe distance between you and surrounding vehicles. It slows you down, speeds you up and even keeps you in your own lane. Meet your ultimate co-pilot with hands-on cruise control.
  • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
Technology and Telematics
  • Smart device mirroring - Smartphone, meet smart car. You can control your device through your vehicle's infotainment system. Smart device mirroring brings together safety and convenience by making it easier to find what you're looking for while keeping your eyes on the road.
Drive home this 2023 Honda Civic EX-L today from Tamaroff Motors in Southfield, MI! Call us at 248-353-1300 to schedule your visit. At only $23,500, it's a deal you don't want to miss. OTHER NOTABLE FEATURES AND OPTIONS YOU SHOULD KNOW ABOUT: Comfort
  • Power reclining driver seat - Lean back. Gain some space between you and the wheel with power reclining driver seat. It lets you adjust the angle of the seatback at the touch of a button for added comfort while you're driving, or for a more comfortable rest while you're pulled over. Settle in, with power reclining driver seat.
Convenience
  • Cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful, until cruise control set the pace. Simply set the desired speed using the steering wheel mounted controls and it will maintain that speed without driver intervention. This can help minimize driver fatigue and improve overall fuel economy. Resting your right foot is right at your fingertips thanks to cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls.
Powertrain and Mechanical
  • Variable valve timing - Change your output. There are a lot of variables in your drive, so why should your engine always operate the same? With variable valve timing, the engine is efficient at both low and high RPM's, so you get better fuel efficiency, cleaner emissions and improved performance. Variable valve timing provides a better drive, every time.
Safety and Security
  • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
  • Brake assist - Stop right there. Something jumps out into the middle of the road and you need to stop now! With brake assist, you will. It uses the speed of the brake pedal's travel to sense panic braking, then applies all available power to boost your stopping power. Brake assist can stop the accident before it is one.

description:
Discover sporty style, impressive efficiency, and modern technology with this 2023 Toyota Corolla Hatchback SE now available at Toyota of Fort Walton Beach. Finished in eye-catching Classic Silver Metallic and powered by a responsive 2.0L I4 engine paired with a smooth CVT transmission, this front-wheel-drive hatchback delivers an excellent balance of performance and fuel economy with an outstanding 32 MPG city and 41 MPG highway. This Recent Arrival is also a CARFAX One-Owner vehicle, giving you added peace of mind and long-term reliability.

Designed for drivers who want versatility without sacrificing fun, this Corolla Hatchback SE features a sporty exterior profile, 16-inch 10-spoke aluminum wheels, body-color bumpers, a rear spoiler, and heated power mirrors. Its compact size makes it ideal for city driving, while the hatchback design offers flexible cargo space for weekend adventures.

Inside, youll enjoy a thoughtfully crafted cabin equipped with sport front seats, fabric seat trim, a leather-wrapped steering wheel, and a leather shift knob. Comfort is enhanced with automatic climate control, a front center armrest, rear seat center armrest, and split-folding rear seats that adapt easily to passengers or cargo.

Stay connected and entertained with the 8-inch Toyota Audio Multimedia system, SiriusXM capability, steering wheel-mounted audio controls, and an integrated backup camera. The Corolla Hatchback SE also includes Toyotas advanced safety and driver-assist technologies such as auto high-beam headlights, electronic stability control, traction control, brake assist, and a full airbag system including knee and rear side-impact airbags. Safety Connect with up to a 10-year trial subscription provides added confidence wherever the road takes you.

At Toyota of Fort Walton Beach, we make it easy to purchase with confidence. We research the local market within a 500-mile radius to ensure every vehicle is competitively and fairly priced based on condition, history, and value. After your test drive, ask your product specialist for a detailed market analysis showing data from multiple trusted sources. If you find a similar vehicle for less, well gladly review it and either explain the difference or match the price.

If youre searching for a fuel-efficient hatchback in Fort Walton Beach, a sporty used Toyota Corolla SE, or a reliable compact car near Destin, Niceville, or Pensacola, this 2023 Toyota Corolla Hatchback SE is an excellent choice.

Discover the perfect blend of style, performance, and technology in this 2023 Mazda Mazda3 2.5 S Premium Package with a 6-Speed Manual transmission. This exceptional vehicle is a true testament to Mazda's commitment to crafting automobiles that captivate the senses and deliver an unparalleled driving experience.

• 6-SPEED MANUAL
• Snowflake White Pearl Mica Paint Charge
• Black Lug Nuts & Black Wheel Locks
• Navigation System
• 12 Speakers

Powered by a spirited 2.5L I4 engine and mated to a smooth-shifting 6-speed manual transmission, this Mazda3 delivers an exhilarating and engaging driving experience. With an impressive EPA-estimated 26 MPG in the city and 36 MPG on the highway, you'll enjoy exceptional efficiency without sacrificing performance.

The Mazda3's striking exterior design, featuring the signature Snowflake White Pearl Mica paint, commands attention on the road. The sleek lines and bold accents give this vehicle a refined and sophisticated appearance that is sure to turn heads. Step inside, and you'll be greeted by a spacious and well-appointed cabin that seamlessly blends premium materials and advanced technology.

Indulge in the convenience of the MAZDA CONNECT Infotainment System, which provides intuitive control over your audio, navigation, and connectivity features. The 12-speaker audio system delivers a concert-hall-quality listening experience, while the Heads-Up Display keeps critical information in your line of sight, allowing you to stay focused on the road.

Safety is a top priority in the Mazda3, with an array of advanced driver-assistance features, including Blind Spot Monitoring, Rear Cross-Traffic Alert, and Smart City Brake Support. These cutting-edge technologies work tirelessly to help keep you and your passengers secure on every journey.

This 2023 Mazda Mazda3 2.5 S Premium Package with a 6-Speed Manual transmission is a true gem in our inventory. With its exceptional blend of style, performance, and technology, it's the perfect choice for the discerning driver who demands more from their vehicle. Experience the difference for yourself by scheduling a test drive today.

Discover the Thrill of Driving Electric with the 2023 Nissan LEAF SV Plus

Imagine a driving experience that's not only eco-friendly but also exhilarating. The 2023 Nissan LEAF SV Plus is the answer to your electric vehicle dreams. This stunning silver beauty boasts a range of up to 212 miles, ensuring you can conquer your daily commute and beyond with confidence.

• Simply Amazing. 100% Electric
• up to 212 miles+++
• Navigation system: NissanConnect EV w/Navigation & Services
• 6 Speakers
• Air Conditioning
• Power driver seat
• Remote keyless entry
• 4-Wheel Disc Brakes
• Rear Parking Sensors
• Auto High-beam Headlights

• Heated Front Bucket Seats

Slip behind the wheel and experience the seamless power delivery of the LEAF's electric motor. With instant torque and responsive handling, you'll be in complete control, whether navigating city streets or cruising the open road. And with an impressive 121 MPGe in the city and 98 MPGe on the highway, you can enjoy the thrill of electric driving while minimizing your environmental impact.

The LEAF's advanced technology features elevate your driving experience. The NissanConnect EV system with Navigation and Services keeps you connected and informed, while the Siri Eyes Free integration allows you to stay focused on the road. Heated front seats and a heated steering wheel ensure your comfort, even on the chilliest days.

Safety is a top priority in the LEAF SV Plus. Dual front and side impact airbags, electronic stability control, and a rear parking sensor system work together to provide a secure and confident driving experience. The Nissan Safety Shield 360 suite of driver-assist technologies further enhances your protection, giving you peace of mind on every journey.

This LEAF SV Plus is a local trade-in, offering you the opportunity to own a well-maintained, low-mileage electric vehicle. Don't miss your chance to experience the future of driving. Schedule a test drive today and discover the power and convenience of the 2023 Nissan LEAF SV Plus.

Technology and Telematics

description:
Introducing the 2023 Nissan Leaf SV Plus, a remarkable electric vehicle that redefines the driving experience. With its exceptional efficiency, advanced technology, and impressive array of features, this Leaf is poised to elevate your daily commute and weekend adventures.

Boasting an impressive array of premium features, the 2023 Nissan Leaf SV Plus is a true standout in its class. Some of the highlights include:

- 1 OWNER
- AUTOMATIC CLIMATE CONTROL
- HEATED SEAT
- NAVIGATION
- BLUETOOTH CONNECTION
- APPLE CARPLAY
- ANDROID AUTO
- PREMIUM WHEELS
- AUTOMATIC HEADLIGHTS
- LED HEADLIGHTS
- BACK-UP CAMERA
- 360 SURROUND-VIEW CAMERA SYSTEM
- ADAPTIVE CRUISE CONTROL
- AUTOMATIC EMERGENCY BRAKING
- BLIND SPOT MONITOR
- CROSS-TRAFFIC ALERT
- LANE DEPARTURE WARNING

Beyond the impressive list of features, this Leaf SV Plus offers exceptional efficiency, with an EPA-estimated 121 MPGe in the city and 98 MPGe on the highway. Its all-electric powertrain delivers a smooth, responsive, and eco-friendly driving experience, making it the perfect choice for the environmentally conscious consumer.

The exterior of the 2023 Nissan Leaf SV Plus is equally striking, with a sleek and modern design highlighted by the vibrant Red color. The LED headlights and premium wheels add a touch of sophistication, while the 360 surround-view camera system and adaptive cruise control enhance your driving confidence.

Step inside, and you'll be greeted by a spacious and well-appointed cabin, featuring a host of advanced technology. The NissanConnect infotainment system with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto integration keeps you connected and entertained, while the heated seats and steering wheel ensure your comfort in any weather.

Safety is also a top priority, with features like automatic emergency braking, blind spot monitoring, and lane departure warning working tirelessly to keep you and your passengers secure on the road.

With its exceptional efficiency, advanced technology, and impressive list of features, the 2023 Nissan Leaf SV Plus is a truly remarkable electric vehicle. We invite you to experience the future of driving by scheduling a test drive at our dealership today. Let us show you how this Leaf can transform your daily commute and weekend adventures.

The Leaf's spacious and well-appointed interior further enhances the driving experience. This exceptional 2023 Nissan Leaf SV Plus is not just a vehicle – it's a testament to the future of sustainable transportation.   • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
  • Hands-on cruise control. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful. Cruise control only managed speed, but not distance or safety. Now, with hands-on cruise control, simply set your desired speed and let sensor technology maintain a safe distance between you and surrounding vehicles. It slows you down, speeds you up and even keeps you in your own lane. Meet your ultimate co-pilot with hands-on cruise control.
  • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
Technology and Telematics
  • Smart device mirroring - Smartphone, meet smart car. You can control your device through your vehicle's infotainment system. Smart device mirroring brings together safety and convenience by making it easier to find what you're looking for while keeping your eyes on the road.

Introducing the brand new 2023 Honda Civic LX, the ultimate combination of style, performance, and reliability. This sleek and modern sedan is equipped with a powerful 2.0-liter I4 engine, delivering an impressive 158 horsepower and 138 foot-pounds of torque. With the smooth and efficient CVT transmission, every ride in the Civic LX will be a breeze.

Step into the spacious and comfortable interior, featuring premium materials and advanced technology. The Civic LX is designed to provide you with the utmost comfort and convenience, making every journey a pleasure. From the ergonomic seats to the user-friendly infotainment system, you'll have everything you need at your fingertips.

But the 2023 Honda Civic LX is not just about comfort and convenience, it's also packed with safety features to give you peace of mind on the road. With advanced driver-assist technologies such as lane departure warning, forward collision warning, and adaptive cruise control, you can confidently drive knowing that the Civic has your back.

Not only is the Civic LX practical and reliable, but it also boasts a stunning exterior design. With its bold lines, sleek profile, and modern touches, this sedan is sure to turn heads wherever you go. And with its fuel-efficient engine, you'll not only look good but also save on gas.

Don't miss your chance to own the 2023 Honda Civic LX. With its exceptional performance, advanced technology, and stylish design, it's the perfect car for those who want the best of everything. Visit our dealership today and experience the Civic LX for yourself. Trust us, you won't be disappointed.

Discover the exhilarating 2023 MINI Cooper S Base, a true testament to the brand's commitment to performance and style. With its powerful 2.0L 16V TwinPower Turbo engine, paired with a responsive 7-Speed Automatic transmission and Front-Wheel Drive, this MINI delivers an unforgettable driving experience.

Elevate your commute with the impressive features that set this Cooper S apart:

• Signature Upholstery Package with Chesterfield Leather Upholstery and Silver Checkered Interior Surface
• Touchscreen Media Display for seamless connectivity
• Steering wheel-mounted audio controls for easy access
• Four-wheel independent suspension for a smooth, responsive ride
• Exterior Parking Camera Rear for confident maneuvering
• Apple CarPlay Compatibility for seamless smartphone integration

The Cooper S's striking White exterior, complemented by the 16" Revolite Spoke Spectre Gray alloy wheels, exudes a bold and sporty presence. Step inside and be captivated by the premium SensaTec Leatherette upholstery, enhancing the cabin's luxurious ambiance.

Enjoy the convenience of features like Remote Keyless Entry, Automatic Climate Control, and a Rear Window Defroster, all while staying connected with the MINI Connected infotainment system. The Cooper S also boasts a suite of advanced safety technologies, including ABS Brakes, Dual Front Impact Airbags, and Electronic Stability Control, ensuring your peace of mind on every journey.

With an EPA-estimated 28 MPG in the city and 38 MPG on the highway, the 2023 MINI Cooper S Base delivers exceptional efficiency without compromising performance. Discover the perfect balance of power, style, and practicality in this remarkable MINI.

This 2024 MINI Hardtop 2 Door Cooper SE, has a British Racing Green IV Metallic exterior and an Black Pearl Light Chequered interior color. 16,705 miles. Stock Number SP4101. No Accidents! One Owner! Important Package and Feature Information Iconic Trim ($5,800 value)
  • Nappa Leather Steering Wheel
  • Power-Folding Mirrors
  • Universal Garage-Door Opener

  • Apple CarPlay Compatibility
  • MINI Connected
  • MINI Connected XL
  • Wireless Charging
  • MINI Navigation
  • Included Content 1
  • Standard Headliner
Convenience
  • Distance pacing cruise control with traffic stop-go. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful. Cruise control only managed speed, but not distance or safety. Now, with Distance pacing cruise control with traffic stop-go, simply set your desired speed and let sensor technology maintain a safe distance between you and the vehicle ahead. It's stop/go feature automatically brings the vehicle to a stop if traffic stops and resumes distance pacing cruise when traffic starts to move again. Distance pacing cruise control with traffic stop-go, your ultimate co-pilot.
Safety and Security
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
  • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
Technology and Telematics
  • Apple CarPlay Compatibility smart device wireless mirroring

description:
Discover the perfect blend of style, performance, and technology in the 2024 Honda Civic Sport. This dynamic compact car is engineered to elevate your driving experience, offering a thrilling combination of sporty handling and impressive efficiency.

At Hyundai of Venice, we use a market-based pricing technology with A.I. that compares our vehicles to similar ones nationwide—factoring in year, mileage, condition, and equipment. Every vehicle is pre-negotiated and priced below market value for a quick, hassle-free sale at a fair price. We also review our prices daily and adjust them based on live market conditions. Because of this data-driven approach and highly competitive pricing, our vehicles sell on average 20 days faster than comparable dealers!

Boasting a 2.0L I4 DOHC 16V engine mated to a 6-Speed Manual transmission, the 2024 Honda Civic Sport delivers an exhilarating driving experience. With 26 city/36 highway MPG, you'll enjoy the perfect balance of power and efficiency. Standout features include:

• Radio: 180-Watt Audio System
• Automatic temperature control
• Remote keyless entry
• Steering wheel mounted audio controls
• Lane Keeping Assist System (LKAS)
• Exterior Parking Camera Rear
• Auto High-beam Headlights
• Apple CarPlay/Android Auto

The interior of the Civic Sport is designed with your comfort and convenience in mind. Sink into the supportive cloth/leatherette seating surfaces, enjoy the tilt and telescoping steering wheel, and stay connected with the intuitive infotainment system. With ample cargo space and a split-folding rear seat, this Civic is ready to accommodate your active lifestyle.

Safety is paramount, and the 2024 Honda Civic Sport delivers with a comprehensive suite of advanced driver-assistance technologies. Dual front and side impact airbags, a knee airbag, and an occupant sensing airbag work together to protect you and your passengers. The Lane Keeping Assist System and Rear Camera further enhance your confidence on the road.

Experience the exceptional blend of style, performance, and technology that the 2024 Honda Civic Sport offers. Visit Hyundai of Venice today and let us demonstrate how this remarkable compact car can elevate your daily driving.

All pricing assumes dealer arranged financing on approved credit. Hyundai of Venice Platinum Protection Plan of $1,295 and $995 CPO Inspection charge (CPO Units only) is not included. Hyundai of Venice also offers various programs periodically, which are mutually exclusive and cannot be combined with other offers. A Dealer Fee of $1299.00, Electronic Titling Fee of $599.95, Private Tag Agency fee of $298.00, and applicable taxes, tags, and government fees are not included in the listed prices. While we strive to represent each vehicle accurately, including color, equipment, and options, we recommend verifying all details before purchase, as we are not liable for errors or omissions. To receive any advertised pricing or specials, a copy of the advertisement must be presented at the time of purchase.

description: Introducing the Nissan Leaf SV Plus, a top-tier hatchback that exemplifies the pinnacle of electric vehicle technology and innovation. At Schomp Nissan, our dedication to exceptional quality extends to our certified pre-owned vehicle offerings, where we abide by the principles of One Price. One Person. One Hour.®When you choose a certified pre-owned Nissan like the Leaf SV Plus, you are selecting a vehicle that has undergone meticulous inspections and rigorous testing to guarantee top-notch performance and reliability. With the assurance of a 7-year/100,000-mile Nissan Certified warranty, you can be confident in the enduring quality of your investment.This sleek and eco-friendly hatchback boasts a range of advanced safety features including standard ABS, Adaptive Cruise Control, Blind Spot Intervention, Forward Collision Warning, Lane Departure Warning, Park Assist, Pedestrian Automatic Emergency Braking, Rear Cross-Traffic Alert, Rear Automatic Emergency Braking, and a Rear Visibility System. Safety is paramount in the Nissan Leaf SV Plus.Under the hood, you'll find a potent 60kW electric motor that delivers efficient and responsive performance. The Leaf SV Plus operates as a Battery Electric Vehicle (BEV) and features a Lithium-Ion battery pack for optimal power delivery. Equipped with Single Motor EV Drive Unit, this vehicle offers a smooth and quiet driving experience.Inside the Leaf SV Plus, you'll discover a comfortable cabin with seating for five passengers across two rows. Safety is further emphasized by the presence of 1st Row (Driver and Passenger) airbags, 1st and 2nd Row curtain airbags, and 1st and 2nd Row side airbags, along with manual seat belts for all occupants.With a distinctive design and a commitment to environmental sustainability, the Nissan Leaf SV Plus is the perfect choice for eco-conscious drivers who seek a balance of style, performance, and peace of mind. Discover the difference at Schomp Nissan, where we simplify the car-buying process and guarantee your satisfaction. Visit us today to explore our range of certified pre-owned vehicles and embark on a new driving journey with confidence.

description:
Land Rover Riverside is delighted to showcase, this Pre-Owned 2024 Toyota Prius Limited dressed in a refined Guardian Gray exterior with a sophisticated interior to match, and with just 24,939 miles on the odometer, this Prius offers an exceptional blend of efficiency, innovation, and comfort.
The 2024 Prius Limited makes a striking first impression with its 19-inch Alloy Wheels, Bi-LED Headlights, and Rain-Sensing Wipers that enhance visibility and style in all weather conditions. Optional features like the Panoramic View Monitor and Advanced Park offer enhanced safety and convenience, while the Digital Rearview Mirror and Dash Cam provide modern driving support and peace of mind.

Step inside and youll be welcomed by a luxurious, tech-forward interior highlighted by SofTex-Trimmed Heated and Ventilated Front Seats, an 8-Way Power Driver Seat with Lumbar Support and Memory, a Heated Steering Wheel, and a 12.3-inch Toyota Audio Multimedia System with Wireless Apple CarPlay and Android Auto compatibility. An immersive JBL 8-Speaker Audio System fills the cabin with crystal-clear sound, while the Qi Wireless Charger and six USB-C ports ensure seamless connectivity on the go.

Engine and Performance: At its heart lies a forward-thinking 2.0L DOHC 16V VVT-i 4-Cylinder Hybrid Synergy Drive System, producing a combined 194 horsepower. The Prius delivers an impressive EPA-estimated 52 MPG combined, offering an economical and eco-conscious drive. The hybrid system is expertly engineered for a balance of performance and efficiency, with smooth acceleration and responsive handling perfect for both city and highway travel.

Key Features:

• Advanced Technology Package: Includes Panoramic View Monitor and Advanced Park for ultimate parking ease.

• Heated Rear Seats: Ensuring comfort for rear passengers in any season.

• Digital Key & Smart Key System: Allows seamless vehicle access and start.

• Wireless Apple CarPlay & Android Auto: Integrate your smartphone effortlessly for calls, navigation, and entertainment.

• JBL Premium Audio: Delivers high-fidelity sound through 8 strategically placed speakers and an integrated amplifier.

• Digital Rearview Mirror & Dash Cam: Modern safety enhancements for real-world driving situations.

This 2024 Toyota Prius Limited redefines what a hybrid can be stylish, sophisticated, and packed with technology. With low mileage and exceptional features, it is a top-tier choice for the discerning eco-conscious driver. Available now at Land Rover Riverside, this Prius awaits a new journey ahead.



Land Rover Riverside is a member of the indiGO Auto Group. Our dealership features a beautiful Land Rover Corporate Identity showroom, fully staffed factory certified service center, parts department, finance department, detail department, and Land Rover accessories boutique. Allow us to also help arrange transportation of your new car directly to your home anywhere in the world. Trade-in proposals are always welcome. If you like this vehicle and have questions, simply call, email, or drop by our location at 8051 Auto Dr, Riverside, CA 92504. We invite you to Activate Your Ownership with us today!

description:
Elevate your driving experience with this exceptional 2024 Honda Civic EX-L. Boasting a sleek gray exterior and a meticulously crafted interior, this sedan is the perfect blend of style and substance.

• Blind Spot Information (BSI) System warning
• Adaptive Cruise Control: Adaptive Cruise Control (ACC) with Low-Speed Follow
• Lane departure: Lane Keeping Assist System (LKAS) active
• Exterior Parking Camera Rear
• Auto High-beam Headlights
• Leather-Trimmed Seating Surfaces
• Heated Front Bucket Seats
• Power moonroof
• 17" Alloy Wheels

Powered by a robust 1.5L I4 DOHC 16V engine and equipped with a fuel-efficient CVT transmission, this Civic delivers an impressive 31 mpg in the city and 39 mpg on the highway, ensuring you'll spend less time at the pump and more time on the open road. The vehicle's four-wheel independent suspension and speed-sensing steering provide a smooth, responsive, and confident driving experience, while the four-wheel disc brakes with ABS ensure reliable stopping power.

Safety is a top priority in the 2024 Civic EX-L, with features like dual front impact airbags, dual front side impact airbags, and an emergency communication system through HondaLink. The Blind Spot Information System and Lane Keeping Assist System work together to enhance your awareness and help you navigate the road with ease.

The interior of this Civic EX-L is equally impressive, with premium leather-trimmed seating surfaces, heated front bucket seats, and a power moonroof that floods the cabin with natural light. The 180-Watt Audio System with 8 speakers and Apple CarPlay/Android Auto integration provide an exceptional multimedia experience, while the dual-zone automatic climate control and rear window defroster ensure your comfort in any weather.

This 2024 Honda Civic EX-L is the perfect balance of style, performance, and technology. With its impressive features and exceptional fuel efficiency, it's a smart choice for the discerning driver. Visit our showroom today to experience the Civic EX-L for yourself and discover how it can elevate your driving experience.

description: Discover the 2024 Toyota Prius LE Hatchback 4D at American Fleet in Fontana, CaliforniaWelcome to American Fleet, your trusted destination for top-quality vehicles in Fontana, San Bernardino, California. If you're searching for a car that perfectly blends fuel efficiency, advanced technology, and modern style, the 2024 Toyota Prius LE Hatchback 4D is the vehicle for you. This hybrid masterpiece is designed to elevate your driving experience while keeping you ahead of the curve in both performance and sustainability. Read on to learn more about why the 2024 Toyota Prius LE Hatchback 4D deserves a place in your driveway.Sleek and Modern Design: The 2024 Toyota Prius LE Hatchback 4DThe 2024 Toyota Prius LE Hatchback 4D is a head-turner with its sleek, aerodynamic design and futuristic appeal. Toyota has redefined the hybrid car's visual identity by incorporating bold lines, a sporty stance, and LED headlamps that illuminate the road with precision and style. Whether you're commuting through San Bernardino or cruising the streets of Fontana, this hatchback ensures you arrive in style.The compact hatchback design is not only visually appealing but also highly practical. Its smartly designed layout maximizes interior space while maintaining a compact footprint, making it ideal for city driving and parking in tight spots. The alloy wheels further enhance its modern look, giving it a premium touch that stands out on the road.Unmatched Hybrid Efficiency with the 2024 Toyota PriusAt the heart of the 2024 Toyota Prius LE Hatchback 4D is a cutting-edge hybrid powertrain that combines a 2.0-liter 4-cylinder engine with an electric motor. This efficient combination delivers an impressive balance of power and fuel economy, making it one of the most eco-friendly vehicles on the market. Whether you're navigating busy streets or embarking on a long road trip, the Prius ensures you go further with fewer stops at the pump.The electronically controlled continuously variable transmission (ECVT) enhances the driving experience by providing smooth and seamless acceleration. The front-wheel-drive (FWD) system ensures optimal handling and stability, giving you confidence behind the wheel in various driving conditions. With the 2024 Toyota Prius, you're not just driving a car, you're driving the future of mobility.Advanced Safety Features for Peace of MindSafety is a top priority in the 2024 Toyota Prius LE Hatchback 4D. This vehicle is equipped with a suite of advanced safety features designed to protect you and your passengers on every journey. The Blind-Spot Monitor helps you change lanes with confidence, while the Lane Departure Alert ensures you stay on course by providing gentle steering assistance if you unintentionally drift out of your lane.The Dynamic Radar Cruise Control takes the stress out of highway driving by maintaining a safe distance from the vehicle ahead, automatically adjusting your speed as needed. The Backup Camera provides a clear view of what's behind you, making parking and reversing safer and easier. With features like Enhanced Stability Control, Traction Control, and Hill Start Assist Control, the Prius is designed to handle a variety of driving conditions with ease.Comfort and Convenience in the 2024 Toyota Prius LE Hatchback 4DStep inside the 2024 Toyota Prius LE Hatchback 4D and experience a cabin designed with your comfort and convenience in mind. The spacious interior offers ample legroom and headroom for both driver and passengers, making every journey a pleasant one. The tilt and telescoping steering wheel allows you to find your perfect driving position, while the electric power steering ensures effortless handling.You'll appreciate the convenience of power windows and power door locks, which make operating the vehicle a breeze. The dual-zone air conditioning system keeps the cabin at your ideal temperature, no matter the weather outside. With its thoughtful design and premium materials, the Prius offers a refined and comfortable driving experience that you'll love.Stay Connected with Cutting-Edge TechnologyThe 2024 Toyota Prius LE Hatchback 4D is packed with advanced technology to keep you connected and entertained on the go. The AM/FM/HD Radio and SiriusXM Satellite provide access to a wide range of music, news, and entertainment options, ensuring there's always something to enjoy during your drive. The Bluetooth Wireless connectivity allows you to make hands-free calls and stream your favorite playlists with ease.With Toyota's Safety Connect, you have access to a suite of connected services that enhance your driving experience and provide added peace of mind. Whether you're navigating the streets of Fontana or exploring San Bernardino County, the Prius ensures you're always in control and connected to what matters most.Enhanced Visibility with LED Headlamps and Daytime Running LightsDriving at night or in low-light conditions is safer and more enjoyable with the 2024 Toyota Prius LE Hatchback 4D. Its LED headlamps provide bright, clear illumination that enhances visibility and reduces eye strain. The Daytime Running Lights improve your vehicle's visibility to other drivers, making it easier for them to see you on the road. These features not only enhance safety but also add a touch of modern sophistication to the Prius's design.Why Buy the 2024 Toyota Prius LE Hatchback 4D from American Fleet?At American Fleet, we take pride in offering a wide selection of high-quality vehicles to meet the needs of our customers in Fontana and the greater San Bernardino area. The 2024 Toyota Prius LE Hatchback 4D is a standout choice for those who value efficiency, innovation, and style. When you choose American Fleet, you can expect a hassle-free car-buying experience, exceptional customer service, and a team dedicated to helping you find the perfect vehicle for your lifestyle.Located in Fontana, California, American Fleet is conveniently situated to serve car buyers throughout San Bernardino County and beyond. Our knowledgeable staff is here to answer your questions, provide expert guidance, and ensure you drive away in a vehicle that meets your needs and exceeds your expectations.Visit American Fleet in Fontana TodayReady to experience the 2024 Toyota Prius LE Hatchback 4D for yourself? Visit American Fleet in Fontana, San Bernardino, California, today. Our friendly team is here to assist you with every step of the car-buying process, from exploring the Prius's features to taking it for a test drive. Don't miss your chance to own one of the most advanced and efficient vehicles on the market. Stop by our dealership or contact us to learn more about the 2024 Toyota Prius LE Hatchback 4D and make it yours today!

This Front Wheel Drive sedan also shows off agile handling in town and achieves nearly 37mpg on the highway. Strong details set our Civic apart from the crowd, with gloss-black alloy wheels, matching mirror caps, LED lighting, and a chrome exhaust finisher leading the way. Comfortably equipped, our Sport cabin can bring a smile to your face with its supportive cloth seats, a foldable back row, a leather-wrapped steering wheel, automatic climate control, sport pedals, keyless access/ignition, and a 12V outlet. An eight-speaker sound system encourages you to tune in and take off, and you can stay connected as you go with a 7-inch touchscreen, Android Auto®/Apple CarPlay®, Bluetooth®, and a 7-inch driver display. description:
Discover the perfect blend of efficiency and style with this 2024 Toyota Prius LE. This exceptional vehicle boasts an impressive array of features that make it an ideal choice for the modern driver.

• CarFax 1-Owner
• Toyota Gold Certified

Elevate your driving experience with the Prius LE's cutting-edge technology and exceptional fuel efficiency. With a city MPG of 57 and a highway MPG of 56, this hybrid powerhouse delivers unparalleled cost savings at the pump. The Exterior Parking Camera Rear provides added peace of mind and convenience, making every maneuver a breeze.

Indulge in the comfort and convenience of this well-equipped Prius. Enjoy the premium audio system, dual-zone automatic climate control, and a host of advanced safety features, including ABS brakes, dual front and side impact airbags, and Electronic Stability Control. The split-folding rear seats and ample cargo space ensure you can easily accommodate all your needs, whether it's a weekend getaway or a daily commute.

As a Toyota Gold Certified vehicle, this Prius LE has undergone a rigorous 160-point inspection and comes with a comprehensive warranty package. Enjoy the peace of mind of a 12-month/12,000-mile limited comprehensive warranty, an 84-month/100,000-mile powertrain limited warranty, and 7 years/100,000 miles of roadside assistance. With a $0 deductible and the backing of Toyota's renowned reliability, you can drive with confidence.

Discover the perfect blend of efficiency, technology, and peace of mind with this 2024 Toyota Prius LE. Experience the joy of owning a meticulously maintained, Toyota-certified vehicle that is ready to enhance your daily driving and exceed your expectations. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate how this Prius can be the perfect fit for your lifestyle.

This vehicle has the following features: Safety and Security
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
  • Hands-on cruise control. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful. Cruise control only managed speed, but not distance or safety. Now, with hands-on cruise control, simply set your desired speed and let sensor technology maintain a safe distance between you and surrounding vehicles. It slows you down, speeds you up and even keeps you in your own lane. Meet your ultimate co-pilot with hands-on cruise control.
  • Hands-off cruise control - Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful. Cruise control only managed speed, but not distance or safety. Now with hands-off cruise control simply set your desired speed and let sensor technology maintain a safe distance between you and surrounding vehicles with minimal steering input from you. It slows you down, speeds you up and even keeps you in your own lane. Meet your ultimate co-pilot with hands-off cruise control.
Technology and Telematics
  • Smart device mirroring - Smartphone, meet smart car. You can control your device through your vehicle's infotainment system. Smart device mirroring brings together safety and convenience by making it easier to find what you're looking for while keeping your eyes on the road.

Introducing the 2019 Toyota Prius LE - a remarkable hybrid that seamlessly blends efficiency, technology, and style. This stunning Red Prius LE is more than just a reliable and eco-friendly ride, it's a testament to Toyota's commitment to innovation.

Boasting an impressive array of features, this Prius LE is equipped to elevate your driving experience. Key highlights include:

• LED DRLs
• Kessy-Keyless Entry with Push Button Start
• Bluetooth
• Autonomous Emergency Braking
• Rearview Camera
• Digital Cockpit
• Backup Camera
• Automatic Headlights
• Blind Spot Monitors
• Phone Operating System Integration
• Touch Screen Controls
• Adaptive Cruise Control
• Lane Assist

Under the hood, the Prius LE is powered by a 1.8L 4-Cylinder DOHC 16V VVT-i engine, delivering an exceptional fuel economy of 54 MPG in the city and 50 MPG on the highway. With its FWD configuration and CVT transmission, this Prius LE offers a smooth and responsive driving experience, making it the perfect companion for your daily commute or weekend adventures.

Stepping inside, you'll be greeted by a well-appointed cabin that caters to your every need. Enjoy the convenience of features like Bluetooth connectivity, a Rearview Camera, and Automatic Headlights, all seamlessly integrated to enhance your driving pleasure. The Digital Cockpit and Touch Screen Controls put vital information and controls at your fingertips, ensuring you stay connected and in command.

Safety is paramount, and the Prius LE delivers with a suite of advanced driver-assistance technologies, including Autonomous Emergency Braking and Blind Spot Monitors. These cutting-edge features work tirelessly to help keep you and your loved ones protected on the road.

With a list price of $20,082, this 2019 Toyota Prius LE represents exceptional value in the hybrid market. Experience the future of eco-friendly driving and discover the joy of owning this remarkable Prius. Visit our showroom today and let us help you make this Prius LE your own.

description:
The 2019 Honda Fit LX is a remarkable compact car that perfectly blends efficiency with performance. With its advanced features and a reliable 1.5L I-4 gasoline direct injection engine, producing 128 horsepower and paired with a smooth continuously variable transmission CVT, it stands out in the subcompact category.

Safety takes precedence in the Honda Fit LX, starting with the rear camera, which provides an enhanced view of the area behind the vehicle, making parking and reversing significantly safer. The inclusion of brake assist is another impressive feature, as it significantly boosts stopping power in emergency situations, ensuring you can respond effectively to unexpected obstacles.

Long drives become more enjoyable with the cruise control system that utilizes steering wheel-mounted controls. This user-friendly feature allows you to maintain a consistent speed without having to keep your foot on the accelerator, reducing fatigue and elevating fuel efficiency. Moreover, the variable valve timing technology optimizes engine performance, delivering superior fuel economy and lower emissions across various driving conditions.

The inline 4-cylinder engine configuration of the Honda Fit LX not only provides a commendable balance between power and fuel efficiency but also results in lower maintenance costs compared to larger engines. The DOHC Dual Overhead Camshaft setup enhances the engines power output and responsiveness, ensuring a lively driving experience.

Connectivity and entertainment options are robust in the Honda Fit LX, featuring wireless audio streaming that allows you to enjoy your favorite playlists without the hassle of cords. The wireless connectivity feature further enhances your driving experience, providing hands-free access to calls so you can stay connected while keeping your focus on the road. For those who love their digital media, the external memory control feature enables easy access and control of music and files stored on hard drives or memory sticks.

Security is paramount in the Honda Fit LX, thanks to the ignition immobilizer system that prevents unauthorized access to the vehicle, giving you peace of mind, especially in urban settings.

In summary, the 2019 Honda Fit LX is an excellent choice for anyone seeking a reliable, efficient, and feature-packed vehicle. With its practical design and advanced safety technologies, it caters to urban drivers and adventure seekers alike, making it a standout option in the compact car market.

When it comes to hybrid efficiency, consistency is key, and this "Homegrown" 2019 Toyota Prius XLE is the gold standard. We have known this car since it had just 230 miles on the odometer, it was sold new here at Napleton's Toyota of Brookfield and has returned to our service bays for nearly every milestone of its life. Boasting a Toyota Silver Certified status and a 1-owner history with zero accidents, this Prius is officially "Well Maintained" by CARFAX standards. With only 52,235 miles, well below the industry average, this fuel-sipping hatchback is ready to provide years of worry-free driving. Read on to see how we've kept this local gem in showroom condition.

Because this vehicle has been "Homegrown" in our shop, it easily qualified for the Toyota Silver Certification. This means it has passed a rigorous 136-point inspection and comes with a 12-month/12,000-mile Limited Powertrain Warranty, along with 24-hour Roadside Assistance.

Our service records show a disciplined history of maintenance. In April 2025, we performed a full fuel injection system flush and induction service to maximize its hybrid economy. At that same visit, we installed four brand-new tires, performed a precision alignment, and balanced the wheels. Most recently, on January 20, 2026, we completed a fresh service and final inspection to ensure it meets our strict standards. It has lived its entire life right here in Wisconsin, and its "Great Reliability" forecast proves that local care makes a world of difference.

Introducing the 2017 Toyota Prius, the perfect combination of efficiency and performance! Equipped with a 1.8L Hybrid I4 engine, producing an impressive 121 horsepower, this Prius is ready to take on any adventure. Its advanced CVT (continuously variable transmission) allows for smooth and seamless acceleration, making every drive a joy.

But that's not all, this Prius is also a hybrid, meaning it not only runs on gasoline but also has an electric motor, resulting in exceptional fuel economy. With an EPA estimated 54 mpg in the city and 50 mpg on the highway, you'll save big at the pump and reduce your carbon footprint.

This 2017 Ford Focus ST, has a Oxford White exterior and an Charcoal Black interior color. 36,587 miles. Stock Number J04707JD. You can connect with us by calling (402) 339-3131.


OTHER NOTABLE FEATURES AND OPTIONS YOU SHOULD KNOW ABOUT:

Equipment Group 400A
  • 6-Speed Manual Transmission
  • Cloth Sport Seats with Unique ST Logo
  • 2.0L GTDI Engine
  • AM/FM/CD/MP3 Radio
  • 18" Y-Rated Summer Tires
  • 18" Rado Gray Alloy Wheels


Convenience
  • Cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful, until cruise control set the pace. Simply set the desired speed using the steering wheel mounted controls and it will maintain that speed without driver intervention. This can help minimize driver fatigue and improve overall fuel economy. Resting your right foot is right at your fingertips thanks to cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls.
Powertrain and Mechanical
  • Variable valve timing - Change your output. There are a lot of variables in your drive, so why should your engine always operate the same? With variable valve timing, the engine is efficient at both low and high RPM's, so you get better fuel efficiency, cleaner emissions and improved performance. Variable valve timing provides a better drive, every time.
Safety and Security
  • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
  • Brake assist - Stop right there. Something jumps out into the middle of the road and you need to stop now! With brake assist, you will. It uses the speed of the brake pedal's travel to sense panic braking, then applies all available power to boost your stopping power. Brake assist can stop the accident before it is one.
Technology and Telematics
  • Selective Internet access - a more focused delivery. Selective internet access allows you to tailor the features for your feed, such as sports scores, local news, or current weather. When it comes to getting what you want, selective internet access is a net gain.

description:
Prime Motors Co is proud to present to you this 2017 Ford Focus RS, finished in Gray and engineered as one of the most exciting all-wheel-drive hot hatches ever produced. Developed with direct input from Ford Performance, the Focus RS delivers rally-inspired capability, sharp handling, and serious turbocharged power in a practical four-door hatchback platform. Power comes from Fords 2.3L turbocharged EcoBoost inline-4 engine, paired with a 6-speed manual transmission and an advanced all-wheel-drive system designed for maximum grip and dynamic performance. With aggressive suspension tuning and performance-focused engineering, the Focus RS offers an engaging, driver-first experience unlike anything else in its class.

Performance
This Focus RS puts drivers first: a 2.3L EcoBoost, 6-speed manual, performance-tuned suspension and high-performance brakes mean crisp response on canyon roads or daily commutes. The AWD system provides confidence in wet Portland weather while keeping the car planted during spirited driving.

Design & Wheels
RS-specific wide-body styling and aggressive aero give the hatchback a purposeful stance and real presence. It rides on 19" forged alloy wheels shod with MICH CUP 2 track summer tiresdesigned for grip and precise feedback.

Interior & Condition
Inside, the driver-focused cockpit, sport seats and performance instrumentation keep controls intuitive and the focus on driving. This used performance hatch shows 93,903 miles and represents a rare chance to own a true motorsport-inspired daily driver.

Ready for a test drive? Visit Prime Motors Co, 2627 SE Holgate Blvd, Portland, OR 97202 or call (971) 512-0578. Open MonSat 10AM7PM (PDT).

description:
Introducing the 2017 Toyota Prius Prime Premium - the ultimate combination of style, efficiency, and advanced technology. This sleek and modern Plug-in Hybrid Electric Vehicle (PHEV) is designed to take you further, without compromising on comfort or convenience.

Featuring a spacious and luxurious interior, the Prius Prime Premium is the perfect choice for those who value both form and function. With ample legroom and headroom, as well as premium materials and finishes, every ride is a comfortable and enjoyable experience.

But the true star of the Prius Prime Premium is its advanced hybrid technology. With a 1.8-liter 4-cylinder engine and a powerful electric motor, this vehicle delivers an impressive 133 MPGe, making it one of the most fuel-efficient cars on the market. Plus, with a total driving range of over 600 miles, you can go further than ever before without having to stop for gas.

But the benefits don't stop there. The Prius Prime Premium also comes equipped with a range of cutting-edge features, including a 7-inch touch screen display, navigation system, and a suite of safety features such as blind spot monitoring and lane departure alert. And with available options like wireless charging and a premium JBL audio system, you can customize your Prius Prime Premium to fit your unique needs and preferences.

description: . Our 2017 Toyota Prius Four Hatchback that's proudly presented in Hypersonic Red! Powered by a 1.8 Liter 4 Cylinder and an Electric Motor generating a combined 121hp paired with an innovative CVT. This Front Wheel Drive hatch helps you to score nearly 54mpg in the city while providing a quiet, enjoyable driving experience with confident handling. Our lean and low Prius Four is sculpted to aerodynamic perfection and looks terrific with alloy wheels, roof rack, and LED headlights. This outstanding Prius embodies innovative technology, safety, and efficiency. Open the door to our Four trim, and you'll be impressed by the ample cargo capacity, intuitive design, and multiple displays that help you monitor your car's remarkable efficiency. Acquaint yourself with Entune Premium Audio infotainment touchscreen with an integrated backup camera that gives you easy access to navigation, real-time data and apps, a great sound system, Bluetooth® phone/audio, and voice recognition with Siri Eyes Free. You'll also appreciate the indulgence of a massive sunroof, heated front seats with leatherette, Qi-compatible wireless smartphone charging, a Smart-Flow climate control system, pushbutton start, and a 60/40-split folding rear seat. Our Toyota includes a blind-spot monitor, rear cross-traffic alert, and the Star Safety System and Toyota Safety Sense for ultimate peace of mind. Our Prius Four hatchback will take you by surprise, see for yourself! Save this Page and Call for Availability. We Know You Will Enjoy Your Test Drive Toward Ownership! .
